name: Single-Minded Fury
spellDescription: When you dual wield one-handed weapons, you deal 5% additional damage and Slam hits with both weapons.

name: Improved Fire Blast
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Fire Blast spell by 1 sec.

name: Incineration
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Fire Blast, Scorch, Arcane Blast and Cone of Cold spells by 2%.

name: Improved Fireball
spellDescription: Reduces the casting time of your Fireball spell by 0.1 sec.

name: Ignite
spellDescription: Your critical strikes from Fire damage spells cause the target to burn for an additional 8% of your spell's damage over 4 sec.

name: Burning Determination
spellDescription: When Interrupted or Silenced you have a 50% chance to become immune to the next Interrupt or Silence mechanic. Lasts 20 sec.

name: World in Flames
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Flamestrike, Pyroblast, Blast Wave, Dragon's Breath, Living Bomb, Blizzard and Arcane Explosion spells by 2%.

name: Flame Throwing
spellDescription: Increases the range of all Fire spells except Frostfire Bolt by 3 yards.

name: Impact
spellDescription: Gives your damaging spells a 4% chance to cause the next Fire Blast you cast to stun the target for 2 sec.

name: Pyroblast
spellDescription: Hurls an immense fiery boulder that causes 141 to 187 Fire damage and an additional 84 Fire damage over 12 sec.

name: Burning Soul
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Fire spells by 35% and reduces the threat caused by your Fire spells by 10%.

name: Improved Scorch
spellDescription: Increases your chance to critically hit with Scorch, Fireball and Frostfire Bolt by an additional 1% and your damaging Scorch spells have a 33% chance to cause your target to be vulnerable to spell damage, increasing spell critical strike chance against that target by 5% and lasts 30 sec.

name: Molten Shields
spellDescription: Causes your Fire Ward and Frost Ward spells to have a 15% chance to reflect the warded spell while active. In addition, your Molten Armor has a 50% chance to affect ranged and spell attacks.

name: Master of Elements
spellDescription: Your spell criticals will refund 10% of their base mana cost.

name: Playing with Fire
spellDescription: Increases all spell damage caused by 1% and all spell damage taken by 1%.

name: Critical Mass
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Fire spells by 2%.

name: Blast Wave
spellDescription: A wave of flame radiates outward from the caster, damaging all enemies caught within the blast for 154 to 186 Fire damage, knocking them back and dazing them for 6 sec.

name: Blazing Speed
spellDescription: Gives you a 50% chance when hit by a melee attack greater than 5% of your max health to increase your movement speed by 50% and dispel all movement impairing effects. This effect lasts 6 sec.

name: Fire Power
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Fire spells by 4%.

name: Pyromaniac
spellDescription: Increases chance to critically hit by 2% and allows 17% of your mana regeneration to continue while casting.

name: Combustion
spellDescription: When activated, this spell increases your critical strike damage bonus with Fire damage spells by 50%, and causes each of your Fire damage spell hits to increase your critical strike chance with Fire damage spells by 10%. This effect lasts until you have caused 3 non-periodic critical strikes with Fire spells.

name: Molten Fury
spellDescription: Increases damage of all spells against targets with less than 35% health by 6%.

name: Fiery Payback
spellDescription: When below 35% health all damage taken is reduced by 10% and your Pyroblast spell's cast time is reduced by 1.75 secs while the cooldown is increased by 2.5 secs. In addition, melee and ranged attacks made against you have a 5% chance to disarm your attacker's main hand and ranged weapons.

name: Empowered Fire
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Fireball, Frostfire Bolt and Pyroblast spells by an amount equal to 5% of your spell power. In addition, each time your Ignite talent causes damage, you have a 33% chance to regain 2% of your base mana.

name: Firestarter
spellDescription: Dealing damage with Blast Wave and Dragon's Breath now has a 50% chance to make your next Flamestrike spell instant cast and cost no mana. Lasts 10 sec.

name: Dragon's Breath
spellDescription: Targets in a cone in front of the caster take 370 to 430 Fire damage and are Disoriented for 5 sec. Any direct damaging attack will revive targets. Turns off your attack when used.

name: Hot Streak
spellDescription: Any time you score 2 non-periodic spell criticals in a row using Fireball, Fire Blast, Scorch, Living Bomb, or Frostfire Bolt, you have a 33% chance the next Pyroblast spell cast within 10 sec will be instant cast.

name: Burnout
spellDescription: Increases your spell critical damage bonus with all spells by 17% but your non-periodic spell criticals cost an additional 2% of the spell's cost.

name: Living Bomb
spellDescription: The target becomes a Living Bomb, taking 612 Fire damage over 12 sec. After 12 sec or when the spell is dispelled, the target explodes dealing 306 Fire damage to all enemies within 10 yards.

name: Frostbite
spellDescription: Gives your Chill effects a 5% chance to freeze the target for 5 sec.

name: Improved Frostbolt
spellDescription: Reduces the casting time of your Frostbolt spell by 0.1 sec.

name: Ice Floes
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Frost Nova, Cone of Cold, Ice Block and Icy Veins spells by 7%.

name: Ice Shards
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage bonus of your Frost spells by 33%.

name: Frost Warding
spellDescription: Increases the armor and resistances given by your Frost Armor and Ice Armor spells by 25%. In addition, gives your Frost Ward and Fire Ward a 15% chance to negate the warded damage spell and restore mana equal to the damage caused.

name: Precision
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost and increases your chance to hit with spells by 1%.

name: Permafrost
spellDescription: Increases the duration of your Chill effects by 1 sec, reduces the target's speed by an additional 4%, and reduces the target's healing received by 7%.

name: Piercing Ice
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Frost spells by 2%.

name: Icy Veins
spellDescription: Hastens your spellcasting, increasing spell casting speed by 20% and reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting by 100%. Lasts 20 sec.

name: Improved Blizzard
spellDescription: Adds a chill effect to your Blizzard spell. This effect lowers the target's movement speed by 25%. Lasts 1.50 sec.

name: Arctic Reach
spellDescription: Increases the range of all your Frost spells except for Frostfire Bolt, and the radius of your Frost Nova and Cone of Cold spells by 10%.

name: Frost Channeling
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of all spells by 4% and reduces the threat caused by your Frost spells by 4%.

name: Shatter
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of all your spells against frozen targets by 17%.

name: Cold Snap
spellDescription: When activated, this spell finishes the cooldown on all Frost spells you recently cast.

name: Improved Cone of Cold
spellDescription: Increases the damage dealt by your Cone of Cold spell by 15%.

name: Frozen Core
spellDescription: Reduces the damage taken from all spells by 2%.

name: Cold as Ice
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Cold Snap, Ice Barrier and Summon Water Elemental spells by 10%.

name: Winter's Chill
spellDescription: Increases your chance to critically hit with Frostbolt by an additional 1% and gives your Frost damage spells a 33% chance to apply the Winter's Chill effect, which increases the chance spells will critically hit the target by 1% for 15 sec. Stacks up to 5 times.

name: Shattered Barrier
spellDescription: Gives your Ice Barrier spell a 50% chance to freeze all enemies within 10 yds for 8 sec when it is destroyed.

name: Ice Barrier
spellDescription: Instantly shields you, absorbing 438 damage. Lasts 1 min. While the shield holds, spellcasting will not be delayed by damage.

name: Arctic Winds
spellDescription: Increases all Frost damage you cause by 2% and reduces the chance melee and ranged attacks will hit you by 1%.

name: Empowered Frostbolt
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Frostbolt spell by an amount equal to 5% of your spell power and reduces the cast time by 0.1 sec.

name: Fingers of Frost
spellDescription: Gives your Chill effects a 7% chance to grant you the Fingers of Frost effect, which treats your next 2 spells cast as if the target were Frozen. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Brain Freeze
spellDescription: Your Frost damage spells with chilling effects have a 5% chance to cause your next Fireball or Frostfire Bolt spell to be instant cast and cost no mana.

name: Summon Water Elemental
spellDescription: Summon a Water Elemental to fight for the caster for 45 sec.

name: Enduring Winter
spellDescription: Increases the duration of your Summon Water Elemental spell by 5 sec and your Frostbolt spell has a 33% chance to grant up to 10 party or raid members mana regeneration equal to 1% of their maximum mana per 5 sec for 15 sec. This effect cannot occur more often than once every 6 sec.

name: Chilled to the Bone
spellDescription: Increases the damage caused by your Frostbolt, Frostfire Bolt, Deep Freeze and Ice Lance spells by 2% and reduces the movement speed of all chilled targets by an additional 4%.

name: Deep Freeze
spellDescription: Stuns the target for 5 seconds. Only usable on Frozen targets. Deals 1469 to 1741 damage to monsters permanently immune to stuns.

name: Arcane Subtlety
spellDescription: Reduces the chance your helpful spells and damage over time effects will be dispelled by 15% and reduces the threat caused by your Arcane spells by 20%.

name: Arcane Focus
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit by 1% and reduces the mana cost of your Arcane spells by 1%.

name: Arcane Stability
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Arcane Missiles and Arcane Blast by 20%.

name: Arcane Fortitude
spellDescription: Increases your armor by an amount equal to 50% of your Intellect.

name: Magic Absorption
spellDescription: Increases all resistances by 0.5 per level and causes all spells that damage you have a 10% chance to restore 1% of your total mana. 6 second cooldown.

name: Arcane Concentration
spellDescription: Gives you a 2% chance of entering a Clearcasting state after any damage spell hits a target. The Clearcasting state reduces the mana cost of your next damage spell by 100%.

name: Magic Attunement
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Arcane spells by 3 yards and the effect of your Amplify Magic and Dampen Magic spells by 1%.

name: Spell Impact
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Arcane Explosion, Arcane Blast, Blast Wave, Fire Blast, Scorch, Fireball, Ice Lance and Cone of Cold spells by an additional 2%.

name: Student of the Mind
spellDescription: Increases your total Spirit by 4%.

name: Focus Magic
spellDescription: Increases the target's chance to critically hit with spells by 3%. When the target critically hits the caster's chance to critically hit with spells is increased by 3% for 10 sec. Cannot be cast on self.

name: Arcane Shielding
spellDescription: Decreases the mana lost per point of damage taken when Mana Shield is active by 17% and increases the resistances granted by Mage Armor by 25%.

name: Improved Counterspell
spellDescription: Your Counterspell also silences the target for 2 sec.

name: Arcane Meditation
spellDescription: Allows 17% of your mana regeneration to continue while casting.

name: Torment the Weak
spellDescription: Your Frostbolt, Fireball, Frostfire Bolt, Pyroblast, Arcane Missiles, Arcane Blast, and Arcane Barrage abilities deal 4% more damage to snared or slowed targets.

name: Improved Blink
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of Blink by 25% and for 4 sec after casting your chance to be hit by all attacks and spells is reduced by 15%.

name: Presence of Mind
spellDescription: When activated, your next Mage spell with a casting time less than 10 sec becomes an instant cast spell.

name: Arcane Mind
spellDescription: Increases your total Intellect by 3%.

name: Prismatic Cloak
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 2% and reduces the fade time of your Invisibility spell by 1 sec.

name: Arcane Instability
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your spells and your critical strike chance by 1%.

name: Arcane Potency
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your next damaging spell by 15% after gaining Clearcasting or Presence of Mind.

name: Arcane Empowerment
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Arcane Missiles spell by an amount equal to 15% of your spell power and the damage of your Arcane Blast by 3% of your spell power. In addition, increases the damage of all party and raid members within 100 yds by 1%.

name: Arcane Power
spellDescription: When activated, your spells deal 20% more damage while costing 20% more mana to cast. This effect lasts 15 sec.

name: Incanter's Absorption
spellDescription: When your Mana Shield, Frost Ward, Fire Ward, or Ice Barrier absorbs damage your spell damage is increased by 5% of the amount absorbed for 10 sec.

name: Arcane Flows
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Presence of Mind, Arcane Power and Invisibility spells by 15% and the cooldown of your Evocation spell by 1 min.

name: Mind Mastery
spellDescription: Increases spell power by 5% of your total Intellect.

name: Slow
spellDescription: Reduces target's movement speed by 60%, increases the time between ranged attacks by 60% and increases casting time by 30%. Lasts 15 sec. Slow can only affect one target at a time.

name: Missile Barrage
spellDescription: Gives your Arcane Blast a 14% chance, and your Arcane Barrage, Fireball, Frostbolt and Frostfire Bolt spells a 7% chance to reduce the channeled duration of the next Arcane Missiles spell by 2 secs, reduce the mana cost by 100%, and missiles will fire every .5 secs.

name: Netherwind Presence
spellDescription: Increases your spell haste by 2%.

name: Spell Power
spellDescription: Increases critical strike damage bonus of all spells by 25%.

name: Arcane Barrage
spellDescription: Launches several missiles at the enemy target, causing 463 to 564 Arcane damage.

name: Improved Heroic Strike
spellDescription: Reduces the cost of your Heroic Strike ability by 1 rage point.

name: Deflection
spellDescription: Increases your Parry chance by 1%.

name: Improved Rend
spellDescription: Increases the bleed damage done by your Rend ability by 10%.

name: Improved Charge
spellDescription: Increases the amount of rage generated by your Charge ability by 5.

name: Iron Will
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of all Stun and Charm effects used against you by 7%.

name: Tactical Mastery
spellDescription: You retain up to an additional 5 of your rage points when you change stances. Also greatly increases the threat generated by your Bloodthirst and Mortal Strike abilities when you are in Defensive Stance.

name: Improved Overpower
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Overpower ability by 25%.

name: Anger Management
spellDescription: Generates 1 rage per 3 seconds.

name: Impale
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage bonus of your abilities by 10%.

name: Deep Wounds
spellDescription: Your critical strikes cause the opponent to bleed, dealing 16% of your melee weapon's average damage over 6 sec.

name: Two-Handed Weapon Specialization
spellDescription: Increases the damage you deal with two-handed melee weapons by 2%.

name: Taste for Blood
spellDescription: Whenever your Rend ability causes damage, you have a 33% chance of allowing the use of your Overpower ability for 9 sec. 1 charge. This effect will not occur more than once every 6 sec.

name: Poleaxe Specialization
spellDescription: Increases your chance to get a critical strike and the critical damage caused with Axes and Polearms by 1%.

name: Sweeping Strikes
spellDescription: Your next 5 melee attacks strike an additional nearby opponent.

name: Mace Specialization
spellDescription: Your attacks with maces ignore up to 3% of your opponent's armor.

name: Sword Specialization
spellDescription: Gives you a 3% chance to get an extra attack on the same target after hitting your target with your Sword. This effect cannot occur more than once every 6 seconds.

name: Weapon Mastery
spellDescription: Reduces the chance for your attacks to be dodged by 1% and reduces the duration of all Disarm effects used against you by 25%. This does not stack with other Disarm duration reducing effects.

name: Improved Hamstring
spellDescription: Gives your Hamstring ability a 5% chance to immobilize the target for 5 sec.

name: Trauma
spellDescription: Your melee critical strikes increase the effectiveness of Bleed effects on the target by 15% for 1 min.

name: Second Wind
spellDescription: Whenever you are struck by a Stun or Immobilize effect you will generate 18 rage and 5% of your total health over 10 sec.

name: Mortal Strike
spellDescription: A vicious strike that deals weapon damage plus 141 and wounds the target, reducing the effectiveness of any healing by 50% for 10 sec.

name: Strength of Arms
spellDescription: Increases your total Strength and Stamina by 2% and your expertise by 2.

name: Improved Slam
spellDescription: Decreases the swing time of your Slam ability by 0.5 sec.

name: Juggernaut
spellDescription: Your Charge ability is now usable while in combat, but the cooldown on Charge is increased by 5 sec. Following a Charge, your next Slam or Mortal Strike has an additional 25% chance to critically hit if used within 10 sec.

name: Improved Mortal Strike
spellDescription: Increases the damage caused by your Mortal Strike ability by 5% and reduces the cooldown by 0.8 sec.

name: Unrelenting Assault
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Overpower and Revenge abilities by 2 secs and increases the damage done by both abilities by 10%. In addition, if you strike a player with Overpower while they are casting, their magical damage and healing will be reduced by 25% for 6 sec.

name: Sudden Death
spellDescription: Your melee hits have a chance of allowing the use of Execute regardless of the target's health state. This chance increases with every hit until it occurs. In addition, you keep at least 1 rage after using Execute.

name: Endless Rage
spellDescription: You generate 25% more rage from damage dealt.

name: Blood Frenzy
spellDescription: Increases your melee attack speed by 5%. In addition your Rend and Deep Wounds abilities also increase all physical damage caused to that target by 2%.

name: Wrecking Crew
spellDescription: Your melee critical hits Enrage you, increasing all damage caused by 3% for 12 sec. This effect does not stack with Enrage.

name: Bladestorm
spellDescription: Instantly Whirlwind up to 6 nearby targets dealing 120% weapon damage and for the next 6 sec you will perform a whirlwind attack every 1 sec. While under the effects of Bladestorm, you can move but cannot perform any other abilities but you do not feel pity or remorse or fear and you cannot be stopped unless killed.

name: Improved Bloodrage
spellDescription: Increases the rage generated by your Bloodrage ability by 25%.

name: Shield Specialization
spellDescription: Increases your chance to block attacks with a shield by 1% and has a 20% chance to generate 5 rage when a block, dodge, or parry occurs.

name: Improved Thunder Clap
spellDescription: Reduces the cost of your Thunder Clap ability by 1 rage point and increases the damage by 10% and the slowing effect by an additional 4%.

name: Incite
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Heroic Strike, Thunder Clap and Cleave abilities by 5%.

name: Anticipation
spellDescription: Increases your Dodge chance by 1%.

name: Last Stand
spellDescription: When activated, this ability temporarily grants you 30% of your maximum health for 20 sec. After the effect expires, the health is lost.

name: Improved Revenge
spellDescription: Increases damage of your Revenge ability by 30% and causes Revenge to strike an additional target for 50% damage.

name: Shield Mastery
spellDescription: Increases your block value by 15% and reduces the cooldown of your Shield Block ability by 10 sec.

name: Toughness
spellDescription: Increases your armor value from items by 4% and reduces the duration of all movement slowing effects by 10%.

name: Improved Spell Reflection
spellDescription: Reduces the chance you'll be hit by spells by 2% and when the ability is used it will reflect the first spell cast against the 4 closest party members within 10 yards.

name: Improved Disarm
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Disarm ability by 10 sec and causes the target to take an additional 5% damage while disarmed.

name: Puncture
spellDescription: Reduces the rage cost of your Sunder Armor and Devastate abilities by 1.

name: Improved Disciplines
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Shield Wall, Retaliation and Recklessness abilities by 30 secs.

name: Concussion Blow
spellDescription: Stuns the opponent for 5 sec and deals 19 damage (based on attack power).

name: Gag Order
spellDescription: Gives your Shield Bash and Heroic Throw abilities a 50% chance to silence the target for 3 sec and increases the damage of your Shield Slam ability by 5%.

name: One-Handed Weapon Specialization
spellDescription: Increases physical damage you deal when a one-handed melee weapon is equipped by 2%.

name: Improved Defensive Stance
spellDescription:
While in Defensive Stance all spell damage taken is reduced by 3% and the chance you'll be critically hit by monsters' melee attacks is reduced by 3%.

Dodging, Blocking or Parrying an attack has a 50% chance to Enrage you, increasing Physical damage caused by 5% for 12 sec.

name: Vigilance
spellDescription: Focus your protective gaze on a group or raid target, reducing their damage taken by 3% and transfers -10% of the threat they cause to you. In addition, each time they are hit by an attack your Taunt cooldown is refreshed. Lasts 30 min. This effect can only be on one target at a time.(This spell cannot miss)

name: Focused Rage
spellDescription: Reduces the rage cost of your offensive abilities by 1.

name: Vitality
spellDescription: Increases your total Strength by 2%, Stamina by 3% and your Expertise by 2.

name: Safeguard
spellDescription: Reduces damage taken by the target of your Intervene ability by 15% for 6 sec.

name: Warbringer
spellDescription: Your Charge, Intercept and Intervene abilities are now usable while in combat and in any stance. In addition, your Intervene ability will remove all movement impairing effects.

name: Devastate
spellDescription: Sunder the target's armor causing the Sunder Armor effect. In addition, causes 120% of weapon damage plus 58 for each application of Sunder Armor on the target. The Sunder Armor effect can stack up to 5 times.

name: Critical Block
spellDescription: Your successful blocks have a 20% chance to block double the normal amount and increases your chance to critically hit with your Shield Slam ability by an additional 5%.

name: Sword and Board
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Devastate ability by 5% and when your Devastate or Revenge ability deals damage it has a 10% chance of refreshing the cooldown of your Shield Slam ability and reducing its cost by 100% for 5 sec.

name: Damage Shield
spellDescription: Whenever you take damage from or block a melee attack you cause damage equal to 10% of your block value.

name: Shockwave
spellDescription: Sends a wave of force in front of the warrior, causing 37 damage (based on attack power) and stunning all enemy targets within 10 yards in a frontal cone for 4 sec.

name: Armored to the Teeth
spellDescription: Increases your attack power by 1 for every 108 armor value you have.

name: Booming Voice
spellDescription: Increases the area of effect and duration of your Battle Shout, Demoralizing Shout and Commanding Shout by 25%.

name: Cruelty
spellDescription: Increases your chance to get a critical strike with melee weapons by 1%.

name: Improved Demoralizing Shout
spellDescription: Increases the melee attack power reduction of your Demoralizing Shout by 8%.

name: Unbridled Wrath
spellDescription: Gives you a chance to generate an additional rage point when you deal melee damage with a weapon.

name: Improved Cleave
spellDescription: Increases the bonus damage done by your Cleave ability by 40%.

name: Piercing Howl
spellDescription: Causes all enemies within 10 yards to be Dazed, reducing movement speed by 50% for 6 sec.

name: Blood Craze
spellDescription: Regenerates 2% of your total Health over 6 sec after being the victim of a critical strike.

name: Commanding Presence
spellDescription: Increases the melee attack power bonus of your Battle Shout and the health bonus of your Commanding Shout by 5%.

name: Dual Wield Specialization
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your off-hand weapon by 5%.

name: Improved Execute
spellDescription: Reduces the rage cost of your Execute ability by 2.

name: Enrage
spellDescription: Gives you a 30% chance to receive a 2% damage bonus for 12 sec after being the victim of a damaging attack. This effect does not stack with Wrecking Crew.

name: Precision
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit with melee weapons by 1%.

name: Death Wish
spellDescription: When activated you become enraged, increasing your physical damage by 20% but increasing all damage taken by 5%. Lasts 30 sec.

name: Improved Intercept
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Intercept ability by 5 sec.

name: Improved Berserker Rage
spellDescription: The Berserker Rage ability will generate 10 rage when used.

name: Flurry
spellDescription: Increases your attack speed by 8% for your next 3 swings after dealing a melee critical strike.

name: Intensify Rage
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Bloodrage, Berserker Rage, Recklessness and Death Wish abilities by 11%.

name: Bloodthirst
spellDescription: Instantly attack the target causing 25 damage. In addition, the next 3 successful melee attacks will restore 2% of max health. This effect lasts 8 sec. Damage is based on your attack power.

name: Improved Whirlwind
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Whirlwind ability by 10%.

name: Furious Attacks
spellDescription: Your normal melee attacks have a chance to reduce all healing done to the target by 25% for 10 sec. This can stack up to 2 times.

name: Improved Berserker Stance
spellDescription: Increases Strength by 4% and reduces threat caused by 2% while in Berserker Stance.

name: Heroic Fury
spellDescription: Removes any Immobilization effects and refreshes the cooldown of your Intercept ability.

name: Rampage
spellDescription: Increases ranged and melee critical hit chance of all party and raid members within 100 yds by 5%.

name: Bloodsurge
spellDescription: Your Heroic Strike, Bloodthirst, and Whirlwind hits have a 7% chance of making your next Slam instant for 8 sec.

name: Unending Fury
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Slam, Whirlwind and Bloodthirst abilities by 4%.

name: Titan's Grip
spellDescription: Allows you to equip two-handed axes, maces and swords in one hand. While you have a two-handed weapon equipped in one hand, your physical damage done is reduced by 10%.

name: Improved Gouge
spellDescription: Increases the effect duration of your Gouge ability by 0.5 sec.

name: Improved Sinister Strike
spellDescription: Reduces the Energy cost of your Sinister Strike ability by 3.

name: Dual Wield Specialization
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your off-hand weapon by 10%.

name: Improved Slice and Dice
spellDescription: Increases the duration of your Slice and Dice ability by 25%.

name: Deflection
spellDescription: Increases your Parry chance by 2%.

name: Precision
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit with weapon and poison attacks by 1%.

name: Endurance
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Sprint and Evasion abilities by 30 sec and increases your total Stamina by 2%.

name: Riposte
spellDescription: A strike that becomes active after parrying an opponent's attack. This attack deals 150% weapon damage and slows their melee attack speed by 20% for 30 sec. Awards 2 combo point.

name: Close Quarters Combat
spellDescription: Increases your chance to get a critical strike with Daggers and Fist Weapons by 1%.

name: Improved Kick
spellDescription: Gives your Kick ability a 50% chance to silence the target for 2 sec.

name: Improved Sprint
spellDescription: Gives a 50% chance to remove all Movement Impairing effects when you activate your Sprint ability.

name: Lightning Reflexes
spellDescription: Increases your Dodge chance by 2% and gives you 4% melee haste.

name: Aggression
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Sinister Strike, Backstab, and Eviscerate abilities by 3%.

name: Mace Specialization
spellDescription: Your attacks with maces ignore up to 3% of your opponent's armor.

name: Blade Flurry
spellDescription: Increases your attack speed by 20%. In addition, attacks strike an additional nearby opponent. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Hack and Slash
spellDescription: Gives you a 1% chance to get an extra attack on the same target after hitting your target with your Sword or Axe.

name: Weapon Expertise
spellDescription: Increases your Expertise by 5.

name: Blade Twisting
spellDescription: Increases the damage dealt by Sinister Strike and Backstab by 5%, and your damaging melee attacks have a 10% chance to Daze the target for 4 sec.

name: Vitality
spellDescription: Increases your Energy regeneration rate by 8%.

name: Adrenaline Rush
spellDescription: Increases your Energy regeneration rate by 100% for 15 sec.

name: Nerves of Steel
spellDescription: Reduces damage taken while affected by Stun and Fear effects by 15%.

name: Throwing Specialization
spellDescription: Increases the range of Throw and Deadly Throw by 2 yards and gives your Deadly Throw a 10% chance per combo point to interrupt the target for 3 sec.

name: Combat Potency
spellDescription: Gives your successful off-hand melee attacks a 20% chance to generate 5 Energy.

name: Unfair Advantage
spellDescription: Whenever you dodge an attack you gain an Unfair Advantage, striking back for 50% of your main hand weapon's damage. This cannot occur more than once per second.

name: Surprise Attacks
spellDescription: Your finishing moves can no longer be dodged, and the damage dealt by your Sinister Strike, Backstab, Shiv, Hemorrhage and Gouge abilities is increased by 10%.

name: Savage Combat
spellDescription: Increases your total attack power by 2% and all physical damage caused to enemies you have poisoned is increased by 2%.

name: Prey on the Weak
spellDescription: Your critical strike damage is increased by 7% when the target has less health than you (as a percentage of total health).

name: Killing Spree
spellDescription: Step through the shadows from enemy to enemy within 10 yards, attacking an enemy every .5 secs with both weapons until 5 assaults are made, and increasing all damage done by 40% for the duration. Can hit the same target multiple times. Cannot hit invisible or stealthed targets.

name: Improved Eviscerate

name: Remorseless Attacks
spellDescription: After killing an opponent that yields experience or honor, gives you a 20% increased critical strike chance on your next Sinister Strike, Hemorrhage, Backstab, Mutilate, Ambush, or Ghostly Strike. Lasts 20 sec.

name: Malice

name: Ruthlessness
spellDescription: Gives your melee finishing moves a 20% chance to add a combo point to your target.

name: Blood Spatter

name: Puncturing Wounds

name: Vigor
spellDescription: Increases your maximum Energy by 10.

name: Improved Expose Armor

name: Lethality
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage bonus of all combo point-generating abilities that do not require stealth by 6%.

name: Improved Poisons

name: Fleet Footed
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of all movement impairing effects by 15% and increases your movement speed by 8%. This does not stack with other movement speed increasing effects.

name: Cold Blood

name: Improved Kidney Shot

name: Quick Recovery
spellDescription: All healing effects on you are increased by 10%. In addition, your finishing moves refund 40% of their Energy cost when they fail to hit.

name: Seal Fate
spellDescription: Your critical strikes from abilities that add combo points have a 33% chance to add an additional combo point.

name: Murder
spellDescription: Increases all damage caused by 2%.

name: Deadly Brew

name: Overkill
spellDescription: While stealthed, and for 20 seconds after breaking stealth, you regenerate 30% additional energy.

name: Deadened Nerves
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 2%.

name: Focused Attacks
spellDescription: Your melee critical strikes have a 33% chance to give you 2 energy.

name: Find Weakness
spellDescription: Offensive ability damage increased by 2%.

name: Master Poisoner
spellDescription: Increases the critical hit chance of all attacks made against any target you have poisoned by 1%, reduces the duration of all Poison effects applied to you by 17%, and gives Envenom a 33% chance not to consume Deadly Poison.

name: Mutilate
spellDescription: Instantly attacks with both weapons for 100% weapon damage plus an additional 34 with each weapon. Damage is increased by 20% against Poisoned targets. Awards 2 combo points.

name: Turn the Tables
spellDescription: Whenever anyone in your party or raid blocks, dodges, or parries an attack your chance to critically hit with all combo moves is increased by 2% for 8 sec.

name: Cut to the Chase
spellDescription: Your Eviscerate, Envenom and Crimson Tempest abilities have a 33% chance to refresh your Slice and Dice duration to its 5 combo point maximum.

name: Hunger For Blood
spellDescription: Enrages you, increasing all damage caused by 5%. Requires a bleed effect to be active on the target. Lasts 1 min.

name: Relentless Strikes
spellDescription: Your finishing moves have a 4% chance per combo point to restore 25 energy.

name: Master of Deception
spellDescription: Reduces the chance enemies have to detect you while in Stealth mode.

name: Opportunity
spellDescription: Increases the damage dealt with your Backstab, Mutilate, Garrote and Ambush abilities by 10%.

name: Sleight of Hand
spellDescription: Reduces the chance you are critically hit by melee and ranged attacks by 1% and increases the threat reduction of your Feint ability by 10%.

name: Dirty Tricks
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Blind and Sap abilities by 2 yards and reduces the energy cost of your Blind and Sap abilities by 25%.

name: Camouflage
spellDescription: Increases your speed while stealthed by 5% and reduces the cooldown of your Stealth ability by 2 sec.

name: Elusiveness
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Vanish and Blind abilities by 30 sec and your Cloak of Shadows ability by 15 sec.

name: Ghostly Strike
spellDescription: A strike that deals 125% weapon damage (180% if a dagger is equipped) and increases your chance to dodge by 15% for 7 sec. Awards 1 combo point.

name: Serrated Blades
spellDescription: Causes your attacks to ignore up to 3% of your target's Armor and increases the damage dealt by your Rupture ability by 10%.

name: Setup
spellDescription: Gives you a 33% chance to add a combo point to your target after dodging their attack or fully resisting one of their spells. This cannot happen more than once per second.

name: Initiative
spellDescription: Gives you a 33% chance to add an additional combo point to your target when using your Ambush, Garrote, or Cheap Shot ability.

name: Improved Ambush
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Ambush ability by 25%.

name: Heightened Senses
spellDescription: Increases your Stealth detection and reduces the chance you are hit by spells and ranged attacks by 2%.

name: Preparation
spellDescription: When activated, this ability immediately finishes the cooldown on your Evasion, Sprint, Vanish, Cold Blood and Shadowstep abilities.

name: Dirty Deeds
spellDescription: Reduces the Energy cost of your Cheap Shot and Garrote abilities by 10. Additionally, your special abilities cause 10% more damage against targets below 35% health.

name: Hemorrhage
spellDescription: An instant strike that deals 110% weapon damage (160% if a dagger is equipped) and causes the target to hemorrhage, increasing any Physical damage dealt to the target by up to 13. Lasts 10 charges or 15 sec. Awards 1 combo point.

name: Master of Subtlety
spellDescription: Attacks made while stealthed and for 6 seconds after breaking stealth cause an additional 4% damage.

name: Deadliness
spellDescription: Increases your attack power by 2%.

name: Enveloping Shadows
spellDescription: Reduces the damage taken by area of effect attacks by 10%.

name: Premeditation
spellDescription: When used, adds 2 combo points to your target. You must add to or use those combo points within 20 sec or the combo points are lost.

name: Cheat Death
spellDescription: You have a 33% chance that an attack which would otherwise kill you will instead reduce you to 10% of your maximum health. In addition, all damage taken will be reduced by 90% for 3 sec. This effect cannot occur more than once every 90 seconds.

name: Sinister Calling
spellDescription: Increases your total Agility by 5% and increases the percentage damage bonus of Backstab and Hemorrhage by an additional 4%.

name: Waylay
spellDescription: Your Ambush and Backstab hits have a 50% chance to unbalance a target, increasing the time between their melee and ranged attacks by 20%, and reducing movement speed by 50% for 8 sec.

name: Honor Among Thieves
spellDescription: When anyone in your group critically hits with a damage or healing spell or ability, you have a 33% chance to gain a combo point on your current target. This effect cannot occur more than once every second.

name: Shadowstep
spellDescription: Attempts to step through the shadows and reappear behind your enemy and increases movement speed by 70% for 3 sec. The damage of your next ability is increased by 20% and the threat caused is reduced by 50%. Lasts 10 sec.

name: Filthy Tricks
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown by 5 sec and energy cost by 5 of your Tricks of the Trade, Distract and Shadowstep abilities and reduces the cooldown of Preparation by 1.5 min.

name: Slaughter from the Shadows
spellDescription: Reduces the energy cost of your Backstab and Ambush abilities by 4 and the energy cost of your Hemorrhage by 2, and increases all damage done by 1%.

name: Shadow Dance
spellDescription: Enter the Shadow Dance for 8 sec, allowing the use of Sap, Garrote, Ambush, Cheap Shot, Premeditation, Pickpocket and Disarm Trap regardless of being stealthed.

name: Unbreakable Will
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of Stun, Fear, and Silence effects done to you by an additional 6%.

name: Twin Disciplines
spellDescription: Increases the damage and healing done by your instant spells by 1%.

name: Silent Resolve
spellDescription: Reduces the threat generated by your Holy and Discipline spells by 7% and reduces the chance your helpful spells and damage over time effects will be dispelled by 10%.

name: Improved Inner Fire

name: Improved Power Word: Fortitude

name: Martyrdom
spellDescription: Gives you a 50% chance to gain the Focused Casting effect that lasts for 6 sec after being the victim of a melee or ranged critical strike. The Focused Casting effect reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Priest spells and decreases the duration of Interrupt effects by 10%.

name: Meditation
spellDescription: Allows 17% of your mana regeneration to continue while casting.

name: Inner Focus
spellDescription: When activated, reduces the mana cost of your next spell by 100% and increases its critical effect chance by 25% if it is capable of a critical effect.

name: Improved Power Word: Shield

name: Absolution

name: Mental Agility

name: Improved Mana Burn

name: Reflective Shield

name: Mental Strength
spellDescription: Increases your total Intellect by 3%.

name: Soul Warding
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Power Word: Shield ability by 4 sec, and reduces the mana cost of your Power Word: Shield by 15%.

name: Focused Power
spellDescription: Increases damage and healing done by your spells by 2%. In addition, your Mass Dispel cast time is reduced by 0.5 sec.

name: Enlightenment
spellDescription: Increases your total Spirit by 2% and increases your spell haste by 2%.

name: Focused Will
spellDescription: Increases your spell critical effect chance by 1%, and after taking a critical hit you gain the Focused Will effect, reducing all damage taken by 2% and increasing healing effects on you by 3%. Stacks up to 3 times. Lasts 8 sec.

name: Power Infusion
spellDescription: Infuses the target with power, increasing spell casting speed by 20% and reducing the mana cost of all spells by 20%. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Improved Flash Heal

name: Renewed Hope

This effect has a 15 sec cooldown.

name: Rapture
spellDescription: When your Power Word: Shield is completely absorbed or dispelled you are instantly energized with 1.5% of your total mana, and you have a 33% chance to energize your shielded target with 2% total mana, 8 rage, 16 energy or 32 runic power. This effect can only occur once every 12 sec.

name: Aspiration

name: Penance

name: Improved Renew

spellDescription: Reduces all spell damage taken by 2%.

name: Divine Fury

name: Improved Healing

name: Surge of Light
spellDescription: Your spell criticals have a 25% chance to cause your next Smite or Flash Heal spell to be instant cast, cost no mana but be incapable of a critical hit. This effect lasts 10 sec.

name: Spiritual Healing
spellDescription: Increases the amount healed by your healing spells by 4%.

spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage of your Holy Fire, Holy Nova, Penance and Smite by 20%.

name: Radiant Fury
spellDescription:
Your Smite, Holy Fire and the damage of Holy Nova gains an additional 4% of your bonus spell damage effects.

Increase the spell haste of all party and raid members within 50 yards by 1%.

spellDescription: Increases your hit rating by 4% of your Spirit and increases the duration of Holy Fire by 1 sec.

spellDescription:
Creates a Holy Lightwell. 

Lightwell will attempt to heal a nearby party or raid member within 20 yards every second that if they have less than 50% health for 158. 

Lightwell lasts for 30 seconds or until it heals 10 times.

name: Empowered Healing

This sacrifice terminates the effect but heals the target of 50% of their maximum health. Lasts 10 sec.

name: Spirit Tap

name: Improved Mind Blast
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Mind Blast spell by 0.5 sec, and while in Shadowform your Mind Blast also has a 20% chance to reduce all healing done to the target by 20% for 10 sec.

name: Psychic Horror
spellDescription: You terrify the target, causing them to tremble in horror for 3 sec and drop their main hand and ranged weapons for 10 sec.

name: Vampiric Touch
spellDescription: Causes 505 Shadow damage over 15 sec to your target and causes up to 10 party or raid members to gain 1% of their maximum mana per 5 sec when you deal damage from Mind Blast. In addition, if the Vampiric Touch is dispelled it will cause 808 damage to the afflicted target.

name: Pain and Suffering

name: Twisted Faith
spellDescription: Increases your spell power by 8% of your total Spirit, and your damage done by your Mind Flay and Mind Blast is increased by 4% if your target is afflicted by your Shadow Word: Pain.

Dispersion can be cast while stunned, feared or silenced and clears all snare and movement impairing effects when cast, and makes you immune to them while dispersed.

name: Concussion

name: Elemental Warding
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 2%.

name: Elemental Devastation

name: Reverberation
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Shock spells and Wind Shear by 0.2 sec.

name: Elemental Focus

name: Elemental Fury

name: Improved Fire Nova

name: Eye of the Storm
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning, Lava Burst and Hex spells by 23%.

name: Elemental Reach
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning, Fire Nova, and Lava Burst spells by 3 yards, increases the radius of your Thunderstorm spell by 10%, and increases the range of your Flame Shock by 7 yards.

name: Call of Thunder
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning and Thunderstorm spells by an additional 5%.

name: Unrelenting Storm
spellDescription: Regenerate mana equal to 4% of your Intellect every 5 sec, even while casting.

name: Elemental Precision
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit with Fire, Frost and Nature spells by 1% and reduces the threat caused by Fire, Frost and Nature spells by 10%.

name: Lightning Mastery
spellDescription: Reduces the cast time of your Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning, and Lava Burst spells by 0.1 sec.

name: Elemental Mastery

name: Booming Echoes
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Shock spells by an additional 1 sec and increases the direct damage done by them by an additional 10%.

name: Elemental Oath

name: Lightning Overload
spellDescription: Gives your Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning spells a 17% chance to cast a second, similar spell on the same target at no additional cost that causes half damage and no threat.

name: Astral Shift
spellDescription: When stunned, feared or silenced you shift into the Astral Plane reducing all damage taken by 10% for the duration of the stun, fear or silence effect.

name: Totem of Wrath
spellDescription: Summons a Totem of Wrath with 5 health at the feet of the caster. The totem increases spell power by 100 for all party and raid members, and increases the critical strike chance of all attacks by 3% against all enemies within 40 yards. Lasts 5 min.

name: Lava Flows
