name: Shamanism
spellDescription: Your Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning spells gain an additional 7% and your Lava Burst gains an additional 9% of your bonus damage effects.

name: Thunderstorm
spellDescription: You call down a bolt of lightning, energizing you and damaging nearby enemies within 10 yards. Restores 15% mana to you and deals 551 to 629 Nature damage to all nearby enemies, knocking them back 20 yards. This spell is usable while stunned.

name: Improved Healing Wave
spellDescription: Reduces the casting time of your Healing Wave spell by 0.1 sec.

name: Totemic Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your totems by 5%.

name: Improved Reincarnation
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Reincarnation spell by 7 min and increases the amount of health and mana recovered when reincarnating by an additional 10%.

name: Healing Grace
spellDescription: Reduces the threat generated by your healing spells by 5% and reduces the chance your helpful spells and damage over time effects will be dispelled by 10%.

name: Tidal Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your healing spells by 2%.

name: Improved Water Shield
spellDescription: You have a 33% chance to instantly gain mana as if you consumed a Water Shield Orb when you gain a critical effect from your Healing Wave or Riptide spells, a 20% chance when you gain a critical effect from your Lesser Healing Wave spell, and a 13% chance when you gain a critical effect from your Chain Heal spell.

name: Healing Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting any Shaman healing spell by 23%.

name: Tidal Force
spellDescription: Increases the critical effect chance of your Healing Wave, Lesser Healing Wave and Chain Heal by 60%. Each critical heal reduces the chance by 20%. Lasts 20 sec.

name: Ancestral Healing
spellDescription: Reduces your target's physical damage taken by 3% for 15 sec after getting a critical effect from one of your healing spells.

name: Restorative Totems
spellDescription: Increases the effect of your Mana Spring Totem by 7%, and increases the amount healed by your Healing Stream Totem by 15%.

name: Tidal Mastery
spellDescription: Increases the critical effect chance of your healing and lightning spells by 1%.

name: Healing Way
spellDescription: Increases the amount healed by your Healing Wave spell by 8%.

name: Nature's Swiftness
spellDescription: When activated, your next Nature spell with a base casting time less than 10 sec. becomes an instant cast spell. Nature's Swiftness shares a cooldown with Elemental Mastery.

name: Focused Mind
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of any Silence or Interrupt effects used against the Shaman by 10%. This effect does not stack with other similar effects.

name: Purification
spellDescription: Increases the effectiveness of your healing spells by 4%.

name: Nature's Guardian
spellDescription: Whenever a damaging attack brings you below 30% health, your maximum health is increased by 3% for 10 sec and your threat level towards the attacker is reduced. 30 second cooldown.

name: Mana Tide Totem
spellDescription: Summons a Mana Tide Totem with 10% of the caster's health at the feet of the caster for 12 sec that restores 5% of total mana every 3 seconds to group members within 30 yards.

name: Cleanse Spirit
spellDescription: Cleanse the spirit of a friendly target, removing 1 poison effect, 1 disease effect, and 1 curse effect.

name: Blessing of the Eternals
spellDescription: Increases the critical effect chance of your spells by 2%, and increases the chance to apply the Earthliving heal over time effect on the target by 40% when they are at or under 35% total health.

name: Improved Chain Heal
spellDescription: Increases the amount healed by your Chain Heal spell by 10%.

name: Nature's Blessing
spellDescription: Increases your healing by an amount equal to 8% of your Intellect.

name: Ancestral Awakening
spellDescription: When you critically heal with your Healing Wave, Lesser Healing Wave or Riptide you summon an Ancestral spirit to aid you, instantly healing the lowest percentage health friendly party or raid target within 40 yards for 10% of the amount healed.

name: Earth Shield
spellDescription: Protects the target with an earthen shield, reducing casting or channeling time lost when damaged by 30% and causing attacks to heal the shielded target for 123. This effect can only occur once every few seconds. 6 charges. Lasts 10 min. Earth Shield can only be placed on one target at a time and only one Elemental Shield can be active on a target at a time.

name: Improved Earth Shield
spellDescription: Increases the amount of charges for your Earth Shield by 1, and increases the healing done by your Earth Shield by 5%.

name: Tidal Waves
spellDescription: When you cast Chain Heal or Riptide, you have a 33% chance to lower the cast time of your Healing Wave spell by 30% and increase the critical effect chance of your Lesser Healing Wave spell by 25%, until two such spells have been cast. In addition, your Healing Wave gains an additional 7% of your bonus healing effects and your Lesser Healing Wave gains an additional 2% of your bonus healing effects.

name: Riptide
spellDescription: Heals a friendly target for 456 and another 480 over 15 sec. Your next Chain Heal cast on that primary target within 15 sec will consume the healing over time effect and increase the amount of the Chain Heal by 25%.

name: Enhancing Totems
spellDescription: Increases the effect of your Strength of Earth and Flametongue Totems by 5%.

name: Earth's Grasp
spellDescription: Increases the health of your Stoneclaw Totem by 25% and the radius of your Earthbind Totem by 10%, and reduces the cooldown of both totems by 15%.

name: Ancestral Knowledge
spellDescription: Increases your Intellect by 2%.

name: Guardian Totems
spellDescription: Increases the amount of armor increased by your Stoneskin Totem by 10% and reduces the cooldown of your Grounding Totem by 1 sec.

name: Thundering Strikes
spellDescription: Improves your chance to get a critical strike with all spells and attacks by 1%.

name: Improved Ghost Wolf
spellDescription: Reduces the cast time of your Ghost Wolf spell by 1 sec.

name: Improved Shields
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Lightning Shield orbs by 5%, increases the amount of mana gained from your Water Shield orbs by 5% and increases the amount of healing done by your Earth Shield orbs by 5%.

name: Elemental Weapons
spellDescription: Increases the damage caused by your Windfury Weapon effect by 13% increases the spell damage on your Flametongue Weapon by 10% and increases the bonus healing on your Earthliving Weapon by 10%.

name: Shamanistic Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your Shock spells by 45%.

name: Anticipation
spellDescription: Increases your chance to dodge by an additional 1%, and reduces the duration of all Disarm effects used against you by 16%. This does not stack with other Disarm duration reducing effects.

name: Flurry
spellDescription: Increases your attack speed by 10% for your next 3 swings after dealing a melee critical strike.

name: Toughness
spellDescription: Increases your Stamina by 2%, and reduces the duration of movement slowing effects on you by 6%.

name: Improved Windfury Totem
spellDescription: Increases the melee haste granted by your Windfury totem by 2%.

name: Spirit Weapons
spellDescription: Reduces all threat generated by 30% and increases damage done by your Windfury and Flametongue Weapon Enhancements by 5%.

name: Mental Dexterity
spellDescription: Increases your Attack Power by 33% of your Intellect and your chance to hit with spells by 3%.

name: Unleashed Rage
spellDescription: Increases your Expertise by 3, and increases all party and raid members' attack power by 4% while within 100 yards of the Shaman.

name: Weapon Mastery
spellDescription: Increases the damage you deal with all weapons by 4%.

name: Frozen Power
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning, Lava Lash and Shock spells by 5% on targets afflicted by your Frostbrand Attack effect, and your Frost Shock has a 50% chance to root the target in ice for 5 sec. when used on targets at or further than 15 yards from you.

name: Dual Wield Specialization
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit while dual wielding by an additional 2%.

name: Two-Handed Weapon Specialization
spellDescription: Increases your critical strike chance while wielding a Two-Handed Weapon by an additional 2% and increases the damage dealt by Stormstrike by 10%.

name: Stormstrike
spellDescription: Instantly attack with both weapons. In addition, the next 4 sources of Nature damage dealt to the target from the Shaman are increased by 20%. Lasts 12 sec.

name: Static Shock
spellDescription: You have a chance (1.5 PPM) to hit your target with a Lightning Shield orb charge when you deal damage with melee attacks and abilities, and your Lightning Shield gains 2 additional charges.

name: Lava Lash
spellDescription:
You charge your off-hand weapon with lava, instantly dealing 100% off-hand Weapon damage. Damage is increased by 25% if your off-hand weapon is enchanted with Flametongue.

Also teaches you |cFFFFFFFFDual Wield|r.|TInterface\Common\ui-tooltipdivider:12:180:0:0|t
|TInterface\Icons\Ability_DualWield:20:20:0:0|t |cffFFFFFFDual Wield|r
Allows one-hand and off-hand weapons to be equipped in the off-hand.

name: Improved Stormstrike
spellDescription: When you Stormstrike, you have a 50% chance to immediately grant you 20% of your base mana.

name: Mental Quickness
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your instant cast Shaman spells by 4% and increases your spell power by an amount equal to 10% of your attack power.

name: Shamanistic Rage
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 30% and gives your successful melee attacks a chance to regenerate mana equal to 15% of your attack power. This spell is usable while stunned. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Earthen Power
spellDescription: Your Earthbind Totem's pulses have a 50% chance to also remove all snare effects from you and nearby friendly targets, and your Earth Shock reduces enemy attack speed by an additional 5%.

name: Maelstrom Weapon
spellDescription: When you deal damage with a melee weapon, you have a chance to reduce the cast time of your next Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning, Lesser Healing Wave, Healing Wave, Chain Heal, or Hex spell by 20%. Stacks up to 5 times. Lasts 30 sec.

name: Feral Spirit
spellDescription: Summons two Spirit Wolves under the command of the Shaman, lasting 45 sec.

name: Ferocity
spellDescription: Reduces the cost of your Maul, Swipe, Thrash, Claw, Rake and Mangle abilities by 1 Rage or Energy.

name: Feral Aggression
spellDescription: Increases the attack power reduction of your Demoralizing Roar by 8% and the damage caused by your Ferocious Bite by 3%.

name: Feral Instinct
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Swipe and Thrash abilities by 10% and reduces the chance enemies have to detect you while Prowling.

name: Savage Fury
spellDescription: Increases the damage caused by your Claw, Rake, Mangle (Cat), Mangle (Bear), and Maul abilities by 10%.

name: Thick Hide
spellDescription: Increases your Armor contribution from cloth and leather items by 4%.

name: Feral Swiftness
spellDescription: Increases your movement speed by 15% in Cat Form and increases your chance to dodge while in Cat Form, Bear Form and Dire Bear Form by 2%.

name: Survival Instincts
spellDescription: When activated, this ability temporarily grants you 30% of your maximum health for 20 sec while in Bear Form, Cat Form, or Dire Bear Form. After the effect expires, the health is lost.

name: Sharpened Claws
spellDescription: Increases your critical strike chance while in Bear, Dire Bear or Cat Form by 3%.

name: Shredding Attacks
spellDescription: Reduces the energy cost of your Shred ability by 9 and the rage cost of your Lacerate ability by 1.

name: Predatory Strikes
spellDescription: Increases your melee attack power in Cat, Bear and Dire Bear Forms by 50% of your level and 7% of any attack power on your equipped weapon. In addition, your finishing moves have a 7% chance per combo point to make your next Nature spell with a base casting time less than 10 sec. become an instant cast spell.

name: Primal Fury
spellDescription: Gives you a 50% chance to gain an additional 5 Rage anytime you get a critical strike while in Bear and Dire Bear Form and your critical strikes from Cat Form abilities that add combo points have a 50% chance to add an additional combo point.

name: Primal Precision
spellDescription: Increases your Expertise by 5, and you are refunded 40% of the energy cost of a finishing move if it fails to land.

name: Brutal Impact
spellDescription: Increases the stun duration of your Bash and Pounce abilities by 0.5 sec and decreases the cooldown of Bash by 15 sec.

name: Feral Charge
spellDescription:
Teaches Feral Charge (Bear) and Feral Charge (Cat).

Feral Charge (Bear) - Causes you to charge an enemy, immobilizing and interrupting any spell being cast for 4 sec. This ability can be used in Bear Form and Dire Bear Form. 15 second cooldown.

Feral Charge (Cat) - Causes you to leap behind an enemy, dazing them for 3 sec. 30 second cooldown.

name: Nurturing Instinct
spellDescription: Increases your healing spells by up to 35% of your Agility, and increases healing done to you by 10% while in Cat form.

name: Natural Reaction
spellDescription: Increases your dodge while in Bear Form or Dire Bear Form by 2%, and you regenerate 1 rage every time you dodge while in Bear Form or Dire Bear Form.

name: Heart of the Wild
spellDescription: Increases your Intellect by 4%. In addition, while in Bear or Dire Bear Form your Stamina is increased by 2% and while in Cat Form your attack power is increased by 2%.

name: Survival of the Fittest
spellDescription: Increases all attributes by 2%, reduces the chance you'll be critically hit by melee attacks by 2%, and increases your armor contribution from cloth and leather items in Bear Form and Dire Bear Form by 11%.

name: Leader of the Pack
spellDescription: While in Cat, Bear or Dire Bear Form, the Leader of the Pack increases ranged and melee critical chance of all party and raid members within 100 yards by 5%.

name: Improved Leader of the Pack
spellDescription: Your Leader of the Pack ability also causes affected targets to heal themselves for 2% of their total health when they critically hit with a melee or ranged attack. The healing effect cannot occur more than once every 6 sec. In addition, you gain 4% of your maximum mana when you benefit from this heal.

name: Primal Tenacity
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of fear effects by 10%, reduces all damage taken while stunned by 10% while in Cat Form.

name: Protector of the Pack
spellDescription: Increases your attack power by 2% and reduces the damage you take by 4%, while in Bear or Dire Bear Form.

name: Predatory Instincts
spellDescription: While in Cat Form increases your damage from melee critical strikes by 3% and reduces the damage taken from area of effect attacks by 10%.

name: Infected Wounds
spellDescription: Your Shred, Maul, and Mangle attacks cause an Infected Wound in the target. The Infected Wound reduces the movement speed of the target by 16% and the attack speed by 6%. Lasts 12 sec.

name: King of the Jungle
spellDescription: While using your Enrage ability in Bear Form or Dire Bear Form, your damage is increased by 5%, and your Tiger's Fury ability also instantly restores 20 energy. In addition, the mana cost of Bear Form, Cat Form, and Dire Bear Form is reduced by 20%.

name: Mangle
spellDescription: Mangle the target, inflicting damage and causing the target to take additional damage from bleed effects for 1 min. This ability can be used in Cat Form or Dire Bear Form.

name: Improved Mangle
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Mangle (Bear) ability by 0.8 sec., and reduces the energy cost of your Mangle (Cat) ability by 3.

name: Rend and Tear
spellDescription: Increases damage done by your Maul and Shred attacks on bleeding targets by 7%, and increases the critical strike chance of your Ferocious Bite ability on bleeding targets by 8%.

name: Primal Gore
spellDescription: Grants the periodic damage from your Lacerate, Thrash, Rake and Rip abilities the ability to critically hit.

name: Berserk
spellDescription:
When activated, this ability causes your Mangle (Bear) ability to hit up to 3 targets and have no cooldown, and reduces the energy cost of all your Cat Form abilities by 50%. Lasts 15 sec. You cannot use Tiger's Fury while Berserk is active.

Clears the effect of Fear and makes you immune to Fear for the duration.

name: Improved Mark of the Wild
spellDescription: Increases the effects of your Mark of the Wild and Gift of the Wild spells by 20%, and increases all of your total attributes by 1%.

name: Nature's Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Healing Touch, Wrath, Entangling Roots, Cyclone, Nourish, Regrowth and Tranquility by 23%.

name: Furor
spellDescription: Gives you 20% chance to gain 10 Rage when you shapeshift into Bear and Dire Bear Form, and you keep up to 20 of your Energy when you shapeshift into Cat Form, and increases your total Intellect while in Moonkin form by 2%.

name: Naturalist
spellDescription: Reduces the cast time of your Healing Touch spell by 0.1 sec and increases the damage you deal with physical attacks in all forms by 2%.

name: Subtlety
spellDescription: Reduces the threat generated by your restoration spells by 10% and reduces the chance your helpful spells, Moonfire, and Insect Swarm will be dispelled by 10%.

name: Natural Shapeshifter
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of all shapeshifting by 10%.

name: Intensity
spellDescription: Allows 14% of your Mana regeneration to continue while casting and causes your Enrage ability to instantly generate 5 rage.

name: Omen of Clarity
spellDescription: Each of the Druid's damage, healing spells and auto attacks has a chance of causing the caster to enter a Clearcasting state. The Clearcasting state reduces the Mana, Rage or Energy cost of your next damage, healing spell or offensive ability by 100%.

name: Master Shapeshifter
spellDescription:
Grants an effect which lasts while the Druid is within the respective shapeshift form.

Bear Form - Increases physical damage by 2%.

Cat Form - Increases critical strike chance by 2%.

Moonkin Form - Increases spell damage by 2%.

Tree of Life Form - Increases healing by 2%.

name: Tranquil Spirit
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your Healing Touch, Nourish and Tranquility spells by 2%.

name: Improved Rejuvenation
spellDescription: Increases the effect of your Rejuvenation spell by 5%.

name: Nature's Swiftness
spellDescription: When activated, your next Nature spell with a base casting time less than 10 sec. becomes an instant cast spell.

name: Gift of Nature
spellDescription: Increases the effect of all healing spells by 2%.

name: Improved Tranquility
spellDescription: Reduces threat caused by Tranquility by 50%, and reduces the cooldown by 30%.

name: Empowered Touch
spellDescription: Your Healing Touch spell gains an additional 20% and your Nourish spell gains an additional 10% of your bonus healing effects.

name: Nature's Bounty
spellDescription: Increases the critical effect chance of your Regrowth and Nourish spells by 5%.

name: Living Spirit
spellDescription: Increases your total Spirit by 5%.

name: Swiftmend
spellDescription: Consumes a Rejuvenation or Regrowth effect on a friendly target to instantly heal them an amount equal to 12 sec. of Rejuvenation or 18 sec. of Regrowth.

name: Natural Perfection
spellDescription: Your critical strike chance with all spells is increased by 1% and critical strikes against you give you the Natural Perfection effect reducing all damage taken by 2%. Stacks up to 3 times. Lasts 8 sec.

name: Empowered Rejuvenation
spellDescription: The bonus healing effects of your healing over time spells is increased by 7%.

name: Living Seed
spellDescription: When you critically heal your target with Swiftmend, Regrowth, Nourish or Healing Touch spell you have a 33% chance to plant a Living Seed on the target for 30% of the amount healed. The Living Seed will bloom when the target is next attacked. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Revitalize
spellDescription: Your Rejuvenation and Wild Growth spells have a 5% chance to restore 8 Energy, 4 Rage, 1% Mana or 16 Runic Power per tick.

name: Tree of Life
spellDescription:
Grants the ability to shapeshift into the Tree of Life. While in this form you increase healing received by 6% for all party and raid members within 100 yards, reduces the mana cost of your healing over time spells by 20% and you can only cast Restoration spells in addition to Innervate, Barkskin, Nature's Grasp and Thorns spells.

The act of shapeshifting frees the caster of Polymorph and Movement Impairing effects.

name: Improved Tree of Life
spellDescription: Increases your armor contribution from items while in Tree of Life Form by 67%, and increases your healing spell power by 5% of your spirit while in Tree of Life Form.

name: Improved Barkskin
spellDescription: Grants 80% additional armor contribution from cloth and leather items while in Travel Form or while not shapeshifted, increases the damage reduction granted by your Barkskin spell by 5% and reduces the chance your Barkskin is dispelled by 35%.

name: Gift of the Earthmother
spellDescription: Increases your total spell haste by 4% and reduces the global cooldown of your Lifebloom spell by 3%.

name: Wild Growth
spellDescription: Heals up to 5 friendly party or raid members within 15 yards of the target for 686 over 7 sec. The amount healed is applied quickly at first, and slows down as the Wild Growth reaches its full duration.

name: Starlight Wrath
spellDescription: Reduces the cast time of your Wrath, Starfire and Starsurge spells by 0.1 sec.

name: Genesis
spellDescription: Increases the damage and healing done by your periodic spell damage and healing effects by 1%.

name: Moonglow
spellDescription: Reduces the Mana cost of your Moonfire, Starfire, Starfall, Wrath, Healing Touch, Nourish, Regrowth and Rejuvenation spells by 4%.

name: Nature's Majesty
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Wrath, Starfire, Starfall, Starsurge, Nourish and Healing Touch spells by 2%.

name: Improved Moonfire
spellDescription: Increases the damage and critical strike chance of your Moonfire spell by 5%.

name: Brambles
spellDescription: Damage from your Thorns and Entangling Roots increased by 25% and damage done by your Treants increased by 5%. In addition, damage from your Treants and attacks done to you while you have Barkskin active have a 5% chance to daze the target for 3 sec.

name: Nature's Grace
spellDescription: All non-periodic spell criticals have a 33% chance to grace you with a blessing of nature, increasing your spell casting speed by 20% for 3 sec.

name: Nature's Splendor
spellDescription: Increases the duration of your Moonfire and Rejuvenation spells by 3 sec, your Regrowth spell by 6 sec, and your Insect Swarm and Lifebloom spells by 2 sec.

name: Nature's Reach
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Balance spells and Faerie Fire (Feral) ability by 10%, and reduces the threat generated by your Balance spells by 15%.

name: Vengeance
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage bonus of your Starfire, Starfall, Starsurge, Moonfire, and Wrath spells by 33%.

name: Celestial Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Starfire, Starsurge, Hibernate and Hurricane by 23% and increases your total spell haste by 1%.

name: Lunar Guidance
spellDescription: Increases your spell power by 4% of your total Intellect.

name: Insect Swarm
spellDescription: The enemy target is swarmed by insects, decreasing their chance to hit by 3% and causing 203 Nature damage over 14 sec.

name: Improved Insect Swarm
spellDescription: Increases your damage done by your Wrath spell to targets afflicted by your Insect Swarm by 1%, and increases the critical strike chance of your Starfire spell by 1% on targets afflicted by your Moonfire spell.

name: Dreamstate
spellDescription: Regenerate mana equal to 8% of your Intellect every 5 sec, even while casting.

name: Moonfury
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Starfire, Starsurge, Moonfire and Wrath spells by 3%.

name: Balance of Power
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit with all spells by 2% and reduces your damage taken from all spells by 3%.

name: Moonkin Form
spellDescription:
Shapeshift into Moonkin Form. While in this form the armor contribution from items is increased by 370%, damage taken while stunned is reduced by 15%, and all party and raid members within 100 yards have their spell critical chance increased by 5%. Single target spell critical strikes in this form have a chance to instantly regenerate 2% of your total mana. The Moonkin can not cast healing or resurrection spells while shapeshifted.

The act of shapeshifting frees the caster of Polymorph and Movement Impairing effects.

name: Improved Moonkin Form
spellDescription:
|cffFF1A1ARequires |TInterface\Icons\Spell_Nature_ForceOfNature:20:20:0:0|t Moonkin Form (Shapeshift)|r
Your Moonkin Aura also causes affected targets to gain 1% haste and you to gain 17% of your spirit as additional spell damage.

name: Improved Faerie Fire
spellDescription: Your Faerie Fire spell also increases the chance the target will be hit by spell attacks by 1%, and increases the critical strike chance of your damage spells by 1% on targets afflicted by Faerie Fire.

name: Owlkin Frenzy
spellDescription: Attacks done to you while in Moonkin form have a 5% chance to cause you to go into a Frenzy, increasing your damage by 10%, cause you to be immune to pushback while casting Balance spells and restore 2% base mana every 2 sec. Lasts 10 sec.

name: Wrath of Cenarius
spellDescription: Your Starfire and Starsurge gains an additional 10% and your Wrath gains an additional 5% of your bonus damage effects.

name: Eclipse
spellDescription: When you critically hit with Starfire, you have a 33% chance of increasing damage done by Wrath and Starsurge by 40%. When you critically hit with Wrath, you have a 20% chance of increasing your critical strike chance with Starfire and Starsurge by 40%. Each effect lasts 15 sec and each has a separate 30 sec cooldown. Both effects cannot occur simultaneously.

name: Typhoon
spellDescription: You summon a violent Typhoon that does 400 Nature damage when in contact with hostile targets, knocking them back and dazing them for 6 sec.

name: Force of Nature
spellDescription: Summons 3 treants to attack enemy targets for 30 sec.

name: Gale Winds
spellDescription: Increases damage done by your Hurricane and Typhoon spells by 15%, and increases the range of your Cyclone spell by 2 yards.

name: Earth and Moon
spellDescription: Increases your damage done by spells by 2%. In addition, your Wrath, Starfire and Starsurge spells have a 100% chance to apply the Earth and Moon effect, which increases spell damage taken by 4% for 12 sec.

name: Starfall
spellDescription: You summon a flurry of stars from the sky on all targets within 30 yards of the caster, each dealing 145 to 167 Arcane damage. Also causes 26 Arcane damage to all other enemies within 5 yards of the enemy target. Maximum 20 stars. Lasts 10 sec. Shapeshifting into an animal form or mounting cancels the effect. Any effect which causes you to lose control of your character will suppress the starfall effect.

name: Improved Shadow Bolt
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Shadow Bolt spell by 2%, and your Shadow Bolt has a 20% chance to cause your target to be vulnerable to spell damage, increasing spell critical strike chance against that target by 5%. Effect lasts 30 sec.

name: Bane
spellDescription: Reduces the casting time of your Shadow Bolt. Chaos Bolt and Immolate spells by 0.1 sec and your Soul Fire spell by 0.4 sec.

name: Aftermath
spellDescription: Increases the periodic damage done by your Immolate by 3%, and your Conflagrate has a 50% chance to daze the target for 5 sec.

name: Molten Skin
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 2%.

name: Cataclysm
spellDescription: Reduces the Mana cost of your Destruction spells by 4%.

name: Demonic Power
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Succubus' Lash of Pain spell by 3 sec. and reduces the casting time of your Imp's Firebolt spell by 0.25 sec.

name: Shadowburn
spellDescription: Instantly blasts the target for 87 to 99 Shadowflame damage. If the target dies within 5 sec of Shadowburn, and yields experience or honor, the caster gains a Soul Shard.

name: Ruin
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage bonus of your Destruction spells and your Imp's Firebolt spell by 20%.

name: Intensity
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting or channeling any Destruction spell by 35%.

name: Destructive Reach
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Destruction spells by 10% and reduces threat caused by Destruction spells by 10%.

name: Improved Searing Pain
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Searing Pain spell by 4%.

name: Backlash
spellDescription: Increases your critical strike chance with spells by an additional 1% and gives you a 8% chance when hit by a physical attack to reduce the cast time of your next Shadow Bolt or Incinerate spell by 100%. This effect lasts 8 sec and will not occur more than once every 8 seconds.

name: Improved Immolate
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Immolate spell by 10%.

name: Devastation
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Destruction spells by 5%.

name: Nether Protection
spellDescription: After being hit with a spell, you have a 10% chance to gain Nether Protection, reducing all damage by that spell school by 30% for 8 sec.

name: Emberstorm
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Fire and Shadow spells by 3% and reduces the cast time of your Incinerate spell by 0.05 sec.

name: Shield Specialization
spellDescription: Increases your armor value from your equipped Shield by 10% and reduces the chance you'll be critically hit by melee attacks by 2%.

name: Totemic Bond
spellDescription:
Using Stoneclaw Totem while Earthen Guardian is active has a 33% chance to reduce all damage taken by 20% for 2 seconds. 

In addition, 33% of the threat generated by the damage of your Searing Totem and Magma Totem will be redirected to you instead.

name: Earthen Attunement
spellDescription: While Earthen Guardian is active you take 2% less physical damage and 3% less spell damage. Dealing physical damage reduces the target's attack power by 58.

name: Conflagrate
spellDescription: Consumes an Immolate or Shadowflame effect on the enemy target to instantly deal damage equal to 60% of your Immolate or Shadowflame, and causes an additional 40% damage over until cancelled.

name: Soul Leech
spellDescription: Gives your Shadow Bolt, Shadowburn, Chaos Bolt, Soul Fire, Incinerate, Searing Pain and Conflagrate spells a 10% chance to return health equal to 20% of the damage caused.

name: Pyroclasm
spellDescription: When you critically strike with Searing Pain or Conflagrate, your Fire and Shadow spell damage is increased by 2% for 10 sec.

name: Shadow and Flame
spellDescription: Your Shadow Bolt, Shadowburn, Chaos Bolt and Incinerate spells gain an additional 7% of your bonus spell damage effects.

name: Improved Soul Leech
spellDescription: Your Soul Leech effect also restores mana to you and your summoned demon equal to 1% of maximum mana, and has a 50% chance to grant up to 10 party or raid members mana regeneration equal to 1% of maximum mana per 5 sec. Lasts for 15 sec.

name: Backdraft
spellDescription: When you cast Conflagrate, the cast time and global cooldown of your next three Destruction spells is reduced by 10%. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Shadowfury
spellDescription: Shadowfury is unleashed, causing 343 to 407 Shadow damage and stunning all enemies within 8 yds for 3 sec.

name: Empowered Imp
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Imp by 10%, and all critical hits done by your Imp have a 33% chance to increase your spell critical hit chance for your next spell by 100%. This effect lasts 8 sec.

name: Fire and Brimstone
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Incinerate and Chaos Bolt spells to targets afflicted by your Immolate by 4%, and the critical strike chance of your Conflagrate spell is increased by 9%.

name: Chaos Bolt
spellDescription: Sends a bolt of chaotic fire at the enemy, dealing 870 to 1049 Shadowflame damage. Chaos Bolt cannot be resisted, and pierces through all absorption effects.

name: Improved Curse of Agony
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Curse of Agony by 5%.

name: Suppression
spellDescription: Increases your chance to hit with spells by 1%, and reduces the mana cost of your Affliction spells by 2%.

name: Improved Corruption
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Corruption by 2%, and increases the critical strike chance of your Seed of Corruption by 1%.

name: Improved Curse of Weakness
spellDescription: Increases the amount of attack power reduced by your Curse of Weakness by 10%.

name: Improved Drain Soul
spellDescription: Returns 7% of your maximum mana if the target is killed by you while you drain its soul. In addition, your Affliction spells generate 10% less threat.

name: Improved Life Tap
spellDescription: Increases the amount of Mana awarded by your Life Tap spell by 10%.

name: Soul Siphon
spellDescription: Increases the amount drained by your Drain Life and Drain Soul spells by an additional 3% for each of your Affliction effects on the target, up to a maximum of 9% additional effect.

name: Improved Fear
spellDescription: Causes your Fear spell to inflict a Nightmare on the target when the fear effect ends. The Nightmare effect reduces the target's movement speed by 15% for 5 sec.

name: Fel Concentration
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Drain Life, Drain Mana, Drain Soul, Unstable Affliction, and Haunt by 23%.

name: Amplify Curse
spellDescription: Reduces the global cooldown of your Curses by 0.5 sec.

name: Grim Reach
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Affliction spells by 10%.

name: Nightfall
spellDescription:
Gives your Corruption and Drain Life spells a 1% chance to cause you to enter a Shadow Trance state after damaging the opponent. The Shadow Trance state reduces the casting time of your next Shadow Bolt spell by 100%.

This chance increases by an additional 1% every time Shadow Trance does not trigger.

name: Empowered Corruption
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Corruption spell by an amount equal to 12% of your spell power.

name: Shadow Embrace
spellDescription: Your Shadow Bolt and Haunt spells apply the Shadow Embrace effect, increasing all shadow periodic damage dealt to the target by you by 1%, and reduces all periodic healing done to the target by 2%. Lasts for 12 sec. Stacks up to 3 times.

name: Siphon Life
spellDescription: When you deal damage with your Corruption spell, you are instantly healed for 40% of the damage done. In addition, the damage done by your Corruption, Seed of Corruption and Unstable Affliction damage over time effects is increased by 5%.

name: Curse of Exhaustion
spellDescription: Reduces the target's movement speed by 30% for 12 sec. Only one Curse per Warlock can be active on any one target.

name: Improved Felhunter
spellDescription: Your Felhunter regains 4% of its maximum mana each time it hits with its Shadow Bite ability and the cooldown on that ability is reduced by 2 sec. In addition, increases the effect of your Felhunter's Fel Intelligence by 5%.

name: Shadow Mastery
spellDescription: Increases the damage dealt or life drained by your Shadow spells and your Felhunter's Shadow Bite ability by 3%.

name: Eradication
spellDescription: When you deal damage with Corruption, you have 6% chance to increase your spell casting speed by 6% for 10 sec.

name: Contagion
spellDescription: Increases the damage of Curse of Agony, Corruption and Seed of Corruption by 2% and reduces the chance your helpful Affliction spells and damage over time effects will be dispelled by an additional 10%.

name: Dark Pact
spellDescription: Drains 306 of your summoned demon's Mana, returning 100% to you.

name: Improved Howl of Terror
spellDescription: Reduces the casting time of your Howl of Terror spell by 0.8 sec.

name: Malediction
spellDescription: Increases your spell damage by 1%, and increases the periodic critical strike chance of your Corruption and Unstable Affliction spells by 3%.

name: Death's Embrace
spellDescription: Increases the amount drained by your Drain Life by 10% while your health is at or below 20% health, and increases the damage done by your Shadow spells by 4% when your target is at or below 35% health.

name: Unstable Affliction
spellDescription: Shadow energy slowly destroys the target, causing 605 damage over 15 sec. In addition, if the Unstable Affliction is dispelled it will cause 1331 damage to the dispeller and silence them for 5 sec. Only one Unstable Affliction or Immolate per Warlock can be active on any one target.

name: Pandemic
spellDescription: Grants the periodic damage from your Corruption and Unstable Affliction spells the ability to critically hit for 100% increased damage, and increases the critical strike damage bonus of your Haunt spell by 100%.

name: Everlasting Affliction
spellDescription: Your Corruption and Unstable Affliction spells gain an additional 2% of your bonus spell damage, and your Drain Life, Drain Soul, Shadow Bolt, and Haunt spells have a 33% chance to reset the duration of your Corruption spell on the target.

name: Haunt
spellDescription: You send a ghostly soul into the target, dealing 405 to 473 Shadow damage and increasing all damage done by your Shadow damage-over-time effects on the target by 20% for 12 sec. When the Haunt spell ends or is dispelled, the soul returns to you, healing you for 100% of the damage it did to the target.

name: Improved Healthstone
spellDescription: Increases the amount of Health restored by your Healthstone by 10%.

name: Improved Imp
spellDescription: Increases the effect of your Imp's Firebolt, Fire Shield, and Blood Pact spells by 10%.

name: Demonic Embrace
spellDescription: Increases your total Stamina by 4%.

name: Fel Synergy
spellDescription: You have a 50% chance to heal your pet for 15% of the amount of spell damage done by you.

name: Improved Health Funnel
spellDescription: Increases the amount of Health transferred by your Health Funnel spell by 10% and reduces the health cost by 10%. In addition, your summoned Demon takes 15% less damage while under the effect of your Health Funnel.

name: Demonic Brutality
spellDescription: Increases the effectiveness of your Voidwalker's Torment, Consume Shadows, Sacrifice and Suffering spells by 10%, and increases the attack power bonus on your Felguard's Demonic Frenzy effect by 1%.

name: Fel Vitality
spellDescription: Increases the Stamina and Intellect of your Imp, Voidwalker, Succubus, Felhunter and Felguard by 5% and increases your maximum health and mana by 1%.

name: Improved Succubus
spellDescription: Reduces the cast time of your Succubus' Seduction by 22%, and increases the duration of your Succubus' Seduction and Lesser Invisibility spells by 10%.

name: Soul Link
spellDescription: When active, 20% of all damage taken by the caster is taken by your Imp, Voidwalker, Succubus, Felhunter, Felguard, or enslaved demon instead. That damage cannot be prevented. Lasts as long as the demon is active and controlled.

name: Fel Domination
spellDescription: Your next Imp, Voidwalker, Succubus, Felhunter or Felguard Summon spell has its casting time reduced by 5.5 sec and its Mana cost reduced by 50%.

name: Demonic Aegis
spellDescription: Increases the effectiveness of your Demon Armor, Summoner's Armor and Fel Armor spells by 10%.

name: Unholy Power
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Voidwalker, Succubus, Felhunter and Felguard's melee attacks and your Imp's Firebolt by 4%.

name: Master Summoner
spellDescription: Reduces the casting time of your Imp, Voidwalker, Succubus, Felhunter and Fel Guard Summoning spells by 2 sec and the Mana cost by 20%.

name: Mana Feed
spellDescription: When you gain mana from Drain Mana or Life Tap spells, your summoned demon gains 100% of the mana you gain.

name: Master Conjuror
spellDescription: Increases the combat ratings gained from your conjured Firestone and Spellstone by 150%.

name: Master Demonologist
spellDescription:
Grants both the Warlock and the summoned demon an effect as long as that demon is active.

Imp - Increases your Fire damage by 1%, and increases the critical effect chance of your Fire spells by 1%.

Voidwalker - Reduces Physical damage taken by 2%.

Succubus - Increases your Shadow damage by 1%, and increases the critical effect chance of your Shadow spells by 1%.

Felhunter - Reduces all spell damage taken by 2%.

Felguard - Increases all damage done by 1%, and reduces all damage taken by 1%.

Enslaved Demons - Increases all damage done by 1%, and reduces all damage taken by 1%.

name: Molten Core
spellDescription:
Increases the duration of your Immolate by 3 sec, and you have a 4% chance to gain the Molten Core effect when your Corruption deals damage. The Molten Core effect empowers your next 3 Incinerate or Soul Fire spells cast within 15 sec.

Incinerate - Increases damage done by 6% and reduces cast time by 10%.

Soul Fire - Increases damage done by 6% and increases critical strike chance by 5%.

name: Demonic Resilience
spellDescription: Reduces the chance you'll be critically hit by melee and spells by 1% and reduces all damage your summoned demon takes by 5%.

name: Demonic Empowerment
spellDescription:
Grants the Warlock's summoned demon Empowerment.

Imp - Increases the Imp's spell critical strike chance by 20% for 30 sec.

Voidwalker - Increases the Voidwalker's health by 20%, and its threat generated from spells and attacks by 20% for 20 sec.

Succubus - Instantly vanishes, causing the Succubus to go into an improved Invisibility state. The vanish effect removes all stuns, snares and movement impairing effects from the Succubus.

Felhunter - Dispels all magical effects from the Felhunter.

Felguard - Increases the Felguard's attack speed by 20% and breaks all stun, snare and movement impairing effects and makes your Felguard immune to them for 15 sec.

name: Demonic Knowledge
spellDescription: Increases your spell damage by an amount equal to 4% of the total of your active demon's Stamina plus Intellect.

name: Demonic Tactics
spellDescription: Increases melee and spell critical strike chance for you and your summoned demon by 4%.

name: Decimation
spellDescription: When you Shadow Bolt, Incinerate or Soul Fire a target that is at or below 35% health, the cast time of Soul Fire spell is reduced by 20% for 10 sec. Soul Fires cast under the effect of Decimation cost no shard.

name: Improved Demonic Tactics
spellDescription: Increases your summoned demon's critical strike chance equal to 10% of your critical strike chance.

name: Summon Felguard
spellDescription: Summons a Felguard under the command of the Warlock.

name: Nemesis
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Demonic Empowerment, Metamorphosis, and Fel Domination spells by 10%.

name: Demonic Pact
spellDescription: Increases your spell damage by 4%, and your pet's criticals apply the Demonic Pact effect to yourself, party and raid members. Demonic Pact increases spell power by 4% of your Spell Damage for 45 sec. This effect has a 20 sec cooldown. Does not work on Enslaved demons.

name: Metamorphosis
spellDescription: You transform into a Demon for 30 sec. This form increases your armor by 600%, damage by 20%, reduces the chance you'll be critically hit by melee attacks by 6% and reduces the duration of stun and snare effects by 50%. You gain some unique demon abilities in addition to your normal abilities. 3 minute cooldown.

name: Improved Aspect of the Hawk
spellDescription: While Aspect of the Hawk or Dragonhawk is active, all ranged auto-attacks have a 10% chance of increasing ranged attack speed by 3% for 12 sec.

name: Endurance Training
spellDescription: Increases the health of your pet by 2% and your total health by 1%.

name: Focused Fire
spellDescription: All damage caused by you is increased by 1% while your pet is active and the critical strike chance of your pet's special abilities is increased by 10% while Kill Command is active.

name: Improved Aspect of the Monkey
spellDescription: Increases the Dodge bonus of your Aspect of the Monkey and Aspect of the Dragonhawk by 2%.

name: Thick Hide
spellDescription: Increases the armor rating of your pets by 7% and your armor contribution from items by 4%.

name: Improved Revive Pet
spellDescription: Revive Pet's casting time is reduced by 3 sec, mana cost is reduced by 20%, and increases the health your pet returns with by an additional 15%.

name: Pathfinding
spellDescription: Increases the speed bonus of your Aspect of the Cheetah and Aspect of the Pack by 4%, and increases your speed while mounted by 5%. The mounted movement speed increase does not stack with other effects.

name: Aspect Mastery
spellDescription:
Aspect of the Viper - Reduces the damage penalty by 10%.

Aspect of the Monkey - Reduces the damage done to you while active by 5%.

Aspect of the Hawk - Increases the attack power bonus by 30%.

Aspect of the Dragonhawk - Combines the bonuses from Aspect of the Monkey and Hawk.

name: Unleashed Fury
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your pets by 3%.

name: Improved Mend Pet
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your Mend Pet spell by 10% and gives the Mend Pet spell a 25% chance of cleansing 1 Curse, Disease, Magic or Poison effect from the pet each tick.

name: Ferocity
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your pet by 2%.

name: Spirit Bond
spellDescription: While your pet is active, you and your pet will regenerate 1% of total health every 10 sec., and increases healing done to you and your pet by 5%.

name: Intimidation
spellDescription: Command your pet to intimidate the target, causing a high amount of threat and stunning the target for 3 sec. Lasts 15 sec.

name: Bestial Discipline
spellDescription: Increases the Focus regeneration of your pets by 50%.

name: Animal Handler
spellDescription: Increases your pet's attack power by 5%, and increases the duration of your Master's Call effect by 3 sec.

name: Frenzy
spellDescription: Gives your pet a 20% chance to gain a 30% attack speed increase for 8 sec after dealing a critical strike.

name: Ferocious Inspiration
spellDescription: All party and raid members have all damage increased by 1% within 100 yards of your pet. In addition, increases the damage dealt by Arcane Shot and Steady Shot by 3%.

name: Bestial Wrath
spellDescription: Send your pet into a rage causing 50% additional damage for 10 sec. While enraged, the beast does not feel pity or remorse or fear and it cannot be stopped unless killed.

name: Catlike Reflexes
spellDescription: Increases your chance to dodge by 1% and your pet's chance to dodge by an additional 3%. In addition, reduces the cooldown of your Kill Command ability by 10 sec.

name: Invigoration
spellDescription: When your pet scores a critical hit with a special ability, you have a 50% chance to instantly regenerate 2% mana.

name: Serpent's Swiftness
spellDescription: Increases ranged combat attack speed by 7% and your pet's melee attack speed by 7%.

name: Longevity
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Bestial Wrath, Intimidation and Pet Special Abilities by 10%.

name: The Beast Within
spellDescription: Increases all damage you deal by 10% and while your pet is under the effects of Bestial Wrath, you also go into a rage causing 10% additional damage and reducing mana costs of all spells by 50% for 10 sec. While enraged, you do not feel pity or remorse or fear and you cannot be stopped unless killed.

name: Cobra Strikes
spellDescription: You have a 20% chance when you critically hit with Arcane Shot, Steady Shot or Kill Shot to cause your pet's next 2 special attacks to critically hit.

name: Kindred Spirits
spellDescription: Increases your pet's damage by 7% and you and your pet's movement speed by 4% while your pet is active. This does not stack with other movement speed increasing effects.

name: Beast Mastery
spellDescription: You master the art of Beast training, teaching you the ability to tame Exotic pets and increasing your total amount of Pet Skill Points by 4.

name: Improved Tracking
spellDescription: While tracking Beasts, Demons, Dragonkin, Elementals, Giants, Humanoids and Undead, all damage done to those types by the Hunter is increased by 1%.

name: Hawk Eye
spellDescription: Increases the range of your ranged weapons by 2 yards.

name: Savage Strikes
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of Raptor Strike, Mongoose Bite, Counterattack and Carve by 8%.

name: Relentless
spellDescription: Increases your Expertise by 5 and Mongoose Bite, Raptor Strike and Counterattack pierce through 7% of the target's armor.

name: Surefooted
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of movement impairing effects by 10%.

name: Deadly Focus
spellDescription:
Decreases the cooldown of Mongoose Bite by 0.1 seconds.

Mongoose Bite has a 20% chance to enable the use of Counterattack. When used this way Counterattack does not immobilize the target.

name: Entrapment
spellDescription: When your Frost Trap or Snake Trap are triggered you entrap all afflicted targets, preventing them from moving for 2 sec.

name: Hunting for Sport
spellDescription:
Increases the damage of your melee abilities on targets under 35% health by 6%.

The melee haste of all party and raid members within 50 yds is increased by 7%. This effect does not stack with similar effects.

name: Trap Mastery
spellDescription:
Frost Trap and Freezing Trap - Increases the duration by 10%.

Immolation Trap, Explosive Trap and Black Arrow - Increases the periodic damage done by 10%.

Snake Trap - Increases the number of snakes summoned by 2.

name: Survival Instincts
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 2% and increases the critical strike chance of your Arcane Shot, Steady Shot, and Explosive Shot by 2%.

name: Survivalist
spellDescription: Increases your Stamina by 2%.

name: Scatter Shot
spellDescription: A short-range shot that deals 50% weapon damage and disorients the target for 4 sec. Any damage caused will remove the effect. Turns off your attack when used.

name: Deflection
spellDescription: Increases your chance to parry by 1%, and reduces the duration of all Disarm effects used against you by 16%. This does not stack with other Disarm duration reducing effects.

name: Survival Tactics
spellDescription: Reduces the chance your Feign Death ability and all trap spells will be resisted by 2%, and reduces the cooldown of your Disengage ability by 2 sec.

name: T.N.T.
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Explosive Shot, Explosive Trap, Black Arrow and Immolation Trap by 2%.

name: Lock and Load
spellDescription: You have a 33% chance when you trap a target with Freezing Trap, Freezing Arrow or Frost Trap and a 2% chance when you deal periodic damage with your Immolation Trap, Explosive Trap or Black Arrow to cause your next 2 Arcane Shot or Explosive Shot spells to trigger no cooldown, cost no mana and consume no ammo. This effect has a 22 sec cooldown.

name: Hunter vs. Wild
spellDescription: Increases your and your pet's attack power and ranged attack power equal to 10% of your total Stamina.

name: Killer Instinct
spellDescription: Increases your critical strike chance with all attacks by 1%.

name: Counterattack
spellDescription: A strike that becomes active after parrying an opponent's attack. This attack deals 73 damage and immobilizes the target for 5 sec when triggered from parrying an attack. It cannot be blocked, dodged, or parried.

name: Lightning Reflexes
spellDescription: Increases your Agility by 3%.

name: Resourcefulness
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of all traps, melee abilities and Black Arrow by 20% and reduces the cooldown of all traps and Black Arrow by 2 sec.

name: Expose Weakness
spellDescription: Critical strikes have a 33% chance to grant you Expose Weakness. Expose Weakness increases your attack power by 25% of your Agility for 7 sec.

name: Wyvern Sting
spellDescription: A stinging shot that puts the target to sleep for 30 sec. Any damage will cancel the effect. When the target wakes up, the Sting causes 300 Nature damage over 6 sec. Only one Sting per Hunter can be active on the target at a time.

name: Thrill of the Hunt
spellDescription: Gives you a 50% chance to regain 40% of the mana cost of any shot when it critically hits.

name: Spirit Guard
spellDescription: You gain 33% Block Rating equal to your Agility. Ancestral spirits strengthen your shield, further reducing damage taken by blocked attacks by 5%.

name: Master Tactician
spellDescription: Your successful ranged attacks have a 30% chance to increase your critical strike chance with all attacks by 4% and ranged attack speed by 7% for 8 sec.

name: Noxious Stings
spellDescription: If Wyvern Sting is dispelled, the dispeller is also afflicted by Wyvern Sting lasting 16% of the duration remaining, and increases all damage done by you on targets afflicted by your Serpent Sting by 1%.

name: Point of No Escape
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of all of your attacks on targets affected by your Frost Trap, Freezing Trap and Freezing Arrow by 3%.

name: Black Arrow
spellDescription: Fires a Black Arrow at the target, increasing all damage done by you to the target by 6% and dealing 785 Shadow damage over 15 sec.

name: Sniper Training
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Kill Shot ability by 5%, and while standing still for 6 sec, you gain Sniper Training increasing the damage done by your Steady Shot, Aimed Shot, Black Arrow and Explosive Shot by 2% for 15 sec.

name: Hunting Party
spellDescription: Increases your total Agility by an additional 1%, and your Arcane Shot, Explosive Shot and Steady Shot critical strikes have a 33% chance to grant up to 10 party or raid members mana regeneration equal to 1% of the maximum mana per 5 sec. Lasts for 15 sec.

name: Explosive Shot
spellDescription: You fire an explosive charge into the enemy target, dealing 144-172 Fire damage. The charge will blast the target every second for an additional 2 sec.

name: Improved Concussive Shot
spellDescription: Increases the duration of your Concussive Shot's daze effect by 1 sec.

name: Focused Aim
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Steady Shot by 23%, and increases your chance to hit by 1%.

name: Lethal Shots
spellDescription: Increases your critical strike chance with ranged weapons by 1%.

name: Careful Aim
spellDescription: Increases your ranged attack power by an amount equal to 33% of your total Intellect.

name: Improved Hunter's Mark
spellDescription: Increases the bonus attack power granted by your Hunter's Mark ability by 10%, and reduces the mana cost of your Hunter's Mark ability by 33%.

name: Mortal Shots
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike damage bonus of your ranged abilities by 6%.

name: Go for the Throat
spellDescription: Your ranged critical hits cause your pet to generate 25 Focus.

name: Improved Arcane Shot
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Arcane Shot by 5%.

name: Aimed Shot
spellDescription:
An aimed shot that deals 130% ranged weapon damage plus 5 and reduces healing done to that target by 50%. Lasts 10 sec.

This ability shares a cooldown with Multi-Shot.

name: Rapid Killing
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Rapid Fire ability by 30 sec. In addition, after killing an opponent that yields experience or honor, your next Aimed Shot, Arcane Shot or Chimera Shot causes 10% additional damage. Lasts 20 sec.

name: Improved Stings
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Serpent Sting and Wyvern Sting by 10% and the mana drained by your Viper Sting by 10%. In addition, reduces the chance your Sting damage over time effects will be dispelled by 10%.

name: Efficiency
spellDescription: Reduces the Mana cost of your Shots and Stings by 4%.

name: Concussive Barrage
spellDescription: Your successful Chimera Shot and Multi-Shot attacks have a 50% chance to Daze the target for 4 sec.

name: Readiness
spellDescription: When activated, this ability immediately finishes the cooldown on your other Hunter abilities except Bestial Wrath.

name: Barrage
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Quick Shot, Multi-Shot, Aimed Shot, Chimera Shot and Volley spells by 4%.

name: Combat Experience
spellDescription: Increases your total Agility and Intellect by 2%.

name: Ranged Weapon Specialization
spellDescription: Increases the damage you deal with ranged weapons by 2%.

name: Piercing Shots
spellDescription: Your critical Quick, Aimed, Steady, Kill, Chimera and Auto Shots cause the target to bleed for 10% of the damage dealt over 8 sec.

name: Trueshot Aura
spellDescription: Increases the attack power of party and raid members within 100 yards by 10%. Lasts until cancelled.

name: Improved Barrage
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of your Quick Shot, Chimera Shot, Multi-Shot and Aimed Shot abilities by 4% and reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while channeling Volley by 33%.

name: Master Marksman
spellDescription: Increases your critical strike chance by 2%, and reduces the Mana cost of your Steady Shot, Aimed Shot, and Chimera Shot by 10%.

name: Rapid Recuperation
spellDescription: You gain 4% of your mana every 3 sec while under the effect of Rapid Fire, and you gain 1% of your mana every 2 sec for 6 sec when you gain Rapid Killing.

name: Wild Quiver
spellDescription: You have a 7% chance to shoot an additional shot when doing damage with your auto shot, dealing 80% weapon nature damage. Wild Quiver consumes no ammo.

name: Silencing Shot
spellDescription: A shot that deals 50% weapon damage and Silences the target for 3 sec. Non-player victim spellcasting is also interrupted for 3 sec.

name: Improved Steady Shot
spellDescription: Your Steady Shot hits have a 5% chance to increase the damage done by your next Aimed Shot, Arcane Shot or Chimera Shot by 20%, and reduce the mana cost of your next Aimed Shot, Arcane Shot or Chimera Shot by 25%.

name: Marked for Death
spellDescription: Increases your damage done by your shots and the damage done by your pet's special abilities by 2% on marked targets, and increases the critical strike damage bonus of your Quick Shot, Aimed Shot, Arcane Shot, Steady Shot, Kill Shot and Chimera Shot by 4%.

name: Chimera Shot
spellDescription:
You deal 125% weapon damage, refreshing the current Sting on your target and triggering an effect:

Serpent Sting - Instantly deals 40% of the damage done by your Serpent Sting.

Viper Sting - Instantly restores mana to you equal to 60% of the total amount drained by your Viper Sting.

Scorpid Sting - Attempts to Disarm the target for 10 sec. This effect cannot occur more than once per 1 minute.

name: Deflection
spellDescription: Increases your Parry chance by 1%.

name: Benediction
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of all instant cast spells by 2%.

name: Improved Judgements
spellDescription: Decreases the cooldown of your Judgement spells by 1 sec.

name: Heart of the Crusader
spellDescription: In addition to the normal effect, your Judgement spells will also increase the critical strike chance of all attacks made against that target by an additional 1%.

name: Improved Blessing of Might
spellDescription: Increases the attack power bonus of your Blessing of Might by 12%.

name: Vindication
spellDescription: Gives the Paladin's damaging attacks a chance to reduce the target's attack power by 25 for 10 sec.

name: Conviction
spellDescription: Increases your chance to get a critical strike with all spells and attacks by 2%.

name: Seal of Command
spellDescription:
All melee attacks deal 6 to 8 additional Holy damage. When used with attacks or abilities that strike a single target, this additional Holy damage will strike up to 2 additional targets. Lasts 30 min.

Unleashing this Seal's energy will judge an enemy, instantly causing 10 to 12 Holy damage.

name: Pursuit of Justice
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of all Disarm effects by 25% and increases movement and mounted movement speed by 8%. This does not stack with other movement speed increasing effects.

name: Eye for an Eye
spellDescription: All criticals against you cause 5% of the damage taken to the attacker as well. The damage caused by Eye for an Eye will not exceed 50% of the Paladin's total health.

name: Sanctity of Battle
spellDescription: Increases your chance to critically hit with all spells and attacks by 1% and increases the damage caused by Exorcism and Crusader Strike by 5%.

name: Epiphany of Light
spellDescription:
|cffFF1A1ARequires |TInterface\Icons\Spell_Holy_SurgeOfLight:20:20:0:0|t Surge of Light (Rank 2)|r
The periodic damage of Holy Fire has a 4% chance to trigger Surge of Light. In addition, the periodic damage of Holy Fire is increased by 34%.

name: Crusade
spellDescription: Increases all damage caused by 1% and all damage caused against Humanoids, Demons, Undead and Elementals by an additional 1%.

name: Two-Handed Weapon Specialization
spellDescription: Increases the damage you deal with two-handed melee weapons by 2%.

name: Sanctified Retribution
spellDescription: Increases the damage caused by Retribution Aura by 50% and all damage caused by friendly targets affected by any of your Auras is increased by 3%.

name: Vengeance
spellDescription: Gives you a 1% bonus to Physical and Holy damage you deal for 30 sec after dealing a critical strike from a weapon swing, spell, or ability. This effect stacks up to 3 times.

name: Divine Purpose
spellDescription: Reduces your chance to be hit by spells and ranged attacks by 2% and gives your Hand of Freedom spell a 50% chance to remove any Stun effects on the target.

name: The Art of War
spellDescription: Increases the damage of your Judgement, Crusader Strike and Divine Storm abilities by 5% and when your melee attacks critically hit the cast time of your next Flash of Light or Exorcism is reduced by 0.75 sec.

name: Repentance
spellDescription: Puts the enemy target in a state of meditation, incapacitating them for up to 1 min, and removing the effect of Righteous Vengeance. Any damage caused will awaken the target. Usable against Demons, Dragonkin, Giants, Humanoids and Undead.

name: Judgements of the Wise
spellDescription: Your damaging Judgement spells have a 50% chance to grant the Replenishment effect to up to 10 party or raid members mana regeneration equal to 1% of their maximum mana per 5 sec for 15 sec, and to immediately grant you 25% of your base mana.

name: Fanaticism
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of all Judgements capable of a critical hit by 6% and reduces threat caused by all actions by 10% except when under the effects of Righteous Fury.

name: Sanctified Wrath
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance of Hammer of Wrath by 25%, reduces the cooldown of Avenging Wrath by 30 secs and while affected by Avenging Wrath 25% of all damage caused bypasses damage reduction effects.

name: Swift Retribution
spellDescription: Your auras also increase casting, ranged and melee attack speeds by 1%.

name: Promise of the Crusader
spellDescription: Increases the critical strike chance and the chance to hit with Exorcism by 10%.

name: Sheath of Light
spellDescription: Increases your spell power by an amount equal to 10% of your attack power and your critical healing spells heal the target for 20% of the healed amount over 12 seconds.

name: Righteous Vengeance
spellDescription: When any of your melee abilities deal a critical strike, your target will take 10% additional damage over 8 sec.

name: Divine Storm
spellDescription: An instant weapon attack that causes 110% of weapon damage to up to 4 enemies within 8 yards. The Divine Storm heals up to 3 party or raid members totaling 25% of the damage caused.

name: Spiritual Focus
spellDescription: Reduces the pushback suffered from damaging attacks while casting Flash of Light and Holy Light by 14%.

name: Seals of the Pure
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Seal of Righteousness, Seal of Vengeance and Seal of Corruption and their Judgement effects by 3%.

name: Healing Light
spellDescription: Increases the amount healed by your Holy Light, Flash of Light and the effectiveness of Holy Shock spells by 4%.

name: Divine Intellect
spellDescription: Increases your total Intellect by 2%.

name: Unyielding Faith
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of all Fear and Disorient effects by 15%.

name: Aura Mastery
spellDescription: Causes your Concentration Aura to make all affected targets immune to Silence and Interrupt effects and improve the effect of all other auras by 100%. Lasts 6 sec.

name: Illumination
spellDescription: After getting a critical effect from your Flash of Light, Holy Light, or Holy Shock heal spell you have a 20% chance to gain mana equal to 30% of the base cost of the spell.

name: Improved Lay on Hands
spellDescription: Grants the target of your Lay on Hands spell 10% reduced physical damage taken for 15 sec. In addition, the cooldown for your Lay on Hands spell is reduced by 2 min.

name: Improved Concentration Aura
spellDescription: Increases the effect of your Concentration Aura by an additional 5% and while any Aura is active reduces the duration of any Silence or Interrupt effect used against an affected group member by 10%. The duration reduction does not stack with any other effects.

name: Improved Blessing of Wisdom
spellDescription: Increases the effect of your Blessing of Wisdom spell by 10%.

name: Blessed Hands
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of Hand of Freedom, Hand of Sacrifice and Hand of Salvation by 15%, increases the effectiveness of Hand of Salvation by 50% and the effectiveness of Hand of Sacrifice by an additional 5%.

name: Pure of Heart
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of Curse, Disease and Poison effects by 15%.

name: Divine Favor
spellDescription: When activated, gives your next Flash of Light, Holy Light, or Holy Shock spell a 100% critical effect chance.

name: Sanctified Light
spellDescription: Increases the critical effect chance of your Holy Light and Holy Shock spells by 2%.

name: Purifying Power
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of your Cleanse, Purify and Consecration spells by 5% and reduces the cooldown of your Exorcism and Holy Wrath spells by 17%.

name: Holy Power
spellDescription: Increases the critical effect chance of your Holy spells by 1%.

name: Light's Grace
spellDescription: Gives your Holy Light spell a 33% chance to reduce the cast time of your next Holy Light spell by 0.5 sec. This effect lasts 15 sec.

name: Holy Shock
spellDescription: Blasts the target with Holy energy, causing 314 to 340 Holy damage to an enemy, or 433 to 467 healing to an ally.

name: Blessed Life
spellDescription: All attacks against you have a 4% chance to cause half damage.

name: Sacred Cleansing
spellDescription: Your Cleanse spell has a 10% chance to increase the target's resistance to Disease, Magic and Poison by 30% for 10 sec.

name: Holy Guidance
spellDescription: Increases your spell power by 7% of your total Intellect.

name: Divine Illumination
spellDescription: Reduces the mana cost of all spells by 50% for 15 sec.

name: Judgements of the Pure
spellDescription: Increases the damage done by your Seal and Judgement spells by 8%, and your Judgement spells increase your casting and melee haste by 5% for 1 min.

name: Infusion of Light
spellDescription: Your Holy Shock critical hits reduce the cast time of your next Flash of Light by 0.75 sec or increase the critical chance of your next Holy Light by 10%. In addition, causes your Flash of Light to heal targets with Sacred Shield for an additional 50% over 12 sec.

name: Enlightened Judgements
spellDescription: Increases the range of your Judgement of Light and Judgement of Wisdom spells by 15 yards and increases your chance to hit by 2%.

name: Beacon of Light
spellDescription: The target becomes a Beacon of Light to all members of your party or raid within a 60 yard radius. Any direct heals you cast on party or raid members will also heal the Beacon for 100% of the amount healed. Only one target can be the Beacon of Light at a time. Lasts 1 min.

name: Divinity
spellDescription: Increases all healing done by you and all healing effects on you by 1%.

name: Divine Strength
spellDescription: Increases your total Strength by 3%.

name: Stoicism
spellDescription: Reduces the duration of all Stun effects by an additional 10% and reduces the chance your helpful spells and damage over time effects will be dispelled by an additional 10%.

name: Guardian's Favor
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Hand of Protection by 60 sec and increases the duration of your Hand of Freedom by 2 sec.

name: Anticipation
spellDescription: Increases your chance to dodge by 1%.

name: Divine Sacrifice
spellDescription: 30% of all damage taken by party members within 30 yards is redirected to the Paladin (up to a maximum of 40% of the Paladin's health times the number of party members). Damage which reduces the Paladin below 20% health will break the effect. Lasts 10 sec.

name: Improved Righteous Fury
spellDescription: While Righteous Fury is active, damage taken is reduced by 3%.

name: Toughness
spellDescription: Increases your armor value from items by 2% and reduces the duration of all movement slowing effects by 6%.

name: Divine Guardian
spellDescription: When Divine Sacrifice is activated, your party and raid members within 30 yards take 10% reduced damage for 6 sec. In addition, increases the duration of your Sacred Shield by 50% and the amount absorbed by 10%.

name: Improved Hammer of Justice
spellDescription: Decreases the cooldown of your Hammer of Justice spell by 10 sec.

name: Improved Devotion Aura
spellDescription: Increases the armor bonus of your Devotion Aura by 17% and increases the amount healed on any target affected by any of your Auras by 2%.

name: Blessing of Sanctuary
spellDescription: Places a Blessing on the friendly target, reducing damage taken from all sources by 3% for 30 min and increasing strength and stamina by 10%. In addition, when the target blocks, parries, or dodges a melee attack the target will gain 2% of maximum displayed mana. Players may only have one Blessing on them per Paladin at any one time.

name: Reckoning
spellDescription: Gives you a 2% chance after being hit by any damaging attack that the next 4 weapon swings within 8 sec will generate an additional attack.

name: Sacred Duty
spellDescription:
Increases your total Stamina by 2%.

Reduces the chance you'll be critically hit by monsters' melee attacks by 3%.

Reduces the cooldown of your Divine Shield and Divine Protection by 30 sec.

name: One-Handed Weapon Specialization
spellDescription: Increases all damage you deal when a one-handed melee weapon is equipped by 4%.

name: Spiritual Attunement
spellDescription: A passive ability that gives the Paladin mana when healed by other friendly targets' spells. The amount of mana gained is equal to 5% of the amount healed.

name: Holy Shield
spellDescription: Increases chance to block by 30% for 10 sec and deals 79 Holy damage for each attack blocked while active. Each block expends a charge. 8 charges.

name: Ardent Defender
spellDescription: Damage that takes you below 35% health is reduced by 7%. In addition, attacks which would otherwise kill you cause you to be healed by up to 17% of your maximum health (amount healed based on defense). This healing effect cannot occur more often than once every 90 sec.

name: Redoubt
spellDescription: Increases your block value by 15% and damaging melee and ranged attacks against you have a 10% chance to increase your chance to block by 15%. Lasts 10 sec or 5 blocks.

name: Combat Expertise
spellDescription: Increases your Expertise by 2, total Stamina and chance to critically hit by 2%.

name: Touched by the Light
spellDescription: Increases your spell power by an amount equal to 30% of your Strength and increases the amount healed by your critical heals by 15%.

name: Avenger's Shield
spellDescription: Hurls a holy shield at the enemy, dealing 444 to 540 Holy damage, Dazing them and then jumping to additional nearby enemies. Affects 3 total targets. Lasts 10 sec.

name: Guarded by the Light
spellDescription: Spell damage taken is reduced by 3% and gives a 50% chance to refresh the duration of your Divine Plea when you hit an enemy. In addition, your Divine Plea spell is 50% less likely to be dispelled.

name: Shield of the Templar
spellDescription: Reduces all damage taken by 1% and grants your Avenger's Shield a 33% chance to silence your targets for 3 sec.

name: Judgements of the Just
spellDescription: Reduces the cooldown of your Hammer of Justice by 5 sec, increases the duration of your Seal of Justice effect by 0.5 sec and your Judgement spells also reduce the melee attack speed of the target by 10%.

name: Hammer of the Righteous
spellDescription:
Hammer the current target and up to 2 additional nearby targets, causing 4 times your main hand damage per second as Holy damage.

Shares cooldown with Crusader Strike.

name: Carve
spellDescription:
A sweeping attack that strikes up to 5 targets in front of you for 200% weapon damage plus 268.

Increases the damage dealt by your Raptor Strike, Mongoose Bite and Counterattack by 10%. Lasts for 9 sec or until you carve another target.
